<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"},"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem">THEME: <strong>A</strong>chieving <strong>P</strong>eace, <strong>D</strong>ignity and <strong>H</strong>armony through <strong>I</strong>ntegrated <strong>D</strong>evelopment</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5357,"width":"457px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.8","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/final.png?w=478" alt="" class="wp-image-5357" style="aspect-ratio:0.8;object-fit:cover;width:457px;height:auto" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"1000px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>LETTER FROM THE SECRETARY GENERAL</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">"Model UN trains todays students to be tomorrows leaders. Students who do model UN would one day change the world."</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Namaste, Delegates and faculty advisors,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">With these wise words by RYAN VILLANUEVA I, Arav Singh Patel, the Secretary-General, would like to welcome you all to the very first iteration of the Prestigious SHISHUKUNJ NORTH CAMPUS Model United Nations, a journey that will equip you and prepare you for a better future.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">As a 12th grader and a science enthusiast, I fell in love with MUNs back in 7th grade when I participated in my first MUN. Since then, it has become an integral part of my student life. However, MUNs have been a roller coaster ride that has taught me a plethora of new things. Even though I lost my first two MUNs, I never let any shortcomings or obstacles stop me. I kept on learning and growing and finally became the Secretary-General. Strumming the chords of the guitar and playing tennis are my second love after science.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">The past couple of years have been plagued with obstacles and have tested our mettle. The COVID pandemic made us question the term "DEVELOPMENT".</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">It was a time in which even the most developed countries were in a state of havoc. Hundreds of thousands of people perished in a mere two years. The pandemic was an eye-opener, showing the imperfections and major flaws in the way countries function.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">To top that, as soon as the world heaved a sigh of relief, a full-fledged war broke out in Europe, causing mayhem all across the world. This time, the frail and dependent economic systems of the world were revealed.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">With such dangers looming, the worlds fate lies in the hands of the young generation. I believe that the current generation has the potential and ability to solve these issues; the only thing required is a platform and exposure. One of the ways to provide this crucial platform is through the Model United Nations. A MUN fosters the holistic development of youth. At its core, learning, participating, and sharing</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">The Shishukunj North Campus MUN aims to provide an opportunity for students to share their opinions and learn and display essential skills like internationalism, geopolitics, consensus building, deliberation, and negotiation. Another important yet often overlooked skill taught by MUNs is to respect others opinions and persuade them to meet on common ground.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">At North Campus MUN 2023, we offer 15 Dynamic committees with unique and stimulating agendas spanning from Cryptocurrency to the South China Sea Conflict.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">The theme for the Shishukunj North Campus MUN 2023 is-</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Achieving Peace, Dignity, and Harmony through Integrated Development.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">In the Contemporary World, Development has become a necessary evil. The ever-growing population is straining the World. Wars, human rights violations, corruption, coups, and massacres have hindered the overall Human development. Different ways to maintain balance while achieving development is the core of this Theme. All the agendas of the committees herein have been very carefully aligned with the same.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">The Secretariat and the Bureau have been working tirelessly, day and night to make this MUN the best one you will ever experience. But the MUN cant succeed without your active participation, enriching debates and discussions, and comprehensive documentation. Lastly, we cant express how excited we are to watch you debate and come up with innovative solutions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">So, gear up and get ready to learn, grow and create history...together.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Hoping to meet you in October. &nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color"> bientt!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5366,"width":"181px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/grerg.png?w=796" alt="" class="wp-image-5366" style="width:181px;height:auto" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}},"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0.3"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0.3">Arav Singh Patel</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}},"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0.3"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0.3">Secretary General , Under Secretary General: Specialised Agencies and Crisis Director</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}},"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0.3"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0.3">Shishukunj Model United Nations, North Campus, 2023</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"1000px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>LETTER FROM THE DIRECTOR GENERAL</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Dear delegates and Faculty Advisors,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Namaste, it is my distinct honour and pleasure to welcome you all to the very FIRST iteration of The Shishukunj Model United Nations, North Campus.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Since its inception to the present, MUN has contributed to the empowerment of every young mind with information, self-assurance, logical reasoning, and desires for achievement.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">"PEACE, DIGNITY AND HARMONY" stand as a lone beacon of light and happiness in this world of global conflict. All we need to do is encourage humanness in order to solve all the problems of the world and establish peace. Understanding that humanity cannot be lost under any circumstances is important. So, this year our goal is to comprehend humanity in its truest form and go closer to it. Our goal should be to improve committee negotiations and come to agreements on crisis resolution. But in the end, values are what matter. It is now up to us to build a world that upholds the principles outlined in the UN Charter and is passed down to future generations: peace, justice, respect, human rights, tolerance and solidarity.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Ban Ki-Moon once said If we can't all swim together, we will sink. There is no Plan B because there is no planet B. Each time you scan the news being unaware of the fact that the picture of the child hiding behind wires of violence is someplace in another country finding out one's national identity, or each time the headlines of violent attacks and encounters begin to sound repetitive to you, you forfeit a portion of your mankind and compassion. We have begun grouping individuals indiscriminately based on the presumptions that we hold, and we have begun believing that the sole means to achieve peace is via battle, without seeing that by acting so, we are merely asking ourselves the incorrect question. The reality says that diplomacy is rapidly becoming obsolete like an elaborate prank, tranquilly has turned into barely anything more than individuals tolerating adverse beliefs and perverted practises since change is so difficult to come to terms with. Fortunately, we are surrounded by diverse minds, young but mature enough to analyse the problem and present solutions which go beyond the intelligence of even AI.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">We here at this conference aim to make your experience as memorable as possible by presenting you all with 11 committees, each one with a dynamic agenda, with problems you might not know of, from UNSC to Lok Sabha, international to national issues, now it is upon you to do something, let us be 1 step closer to what we dream of.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I really look forward to seeing everyone this October! And I really hope that each one of you takes home a bundle of memories to cherish also, trust me when i say MUNs are the practical representation of learn with fun.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Warm Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0"><br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4547,"width":"144px","height":"92px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/khushi.png?w=353" alt="" class="wp-image-4547" style="width:144px;height:92px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Director General</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Khushi Khanna</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Shishukunj Model United Nations, North Campus, 2023</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:3rem">RESOURCES</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.5rem"></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem">STUDY GUIDES</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3925,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->

<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ii8v3XkSwaOi5BZ28yN2cB3lqtUu7k-F/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unhrc-edited.png" alt="" class="wp-image-4510" style="object-fit:cover;width:200px;height:200px" width="200" height="200" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNHRC</strong></figcaption></figure>

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3906,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1geiQ-Uuko8v9sjRYuGhT7G_O474smPt4/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unccpcj.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-3906" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNCCPCJ</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior LoN]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-aksh-lon/</link>
  <pubDate>Mon, 08 May 2023 10:16:59 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=432</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/league-of-nations-lon-bg.jpeg","id":904,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-904 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/league-of-nations-lon-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60,"className":"is-style-rounded"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:3rem">LEAGUE OF NATIONS</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.5rem">Agenda: Deliberating Over World War II with Emphasis on the Future of Global Institutions</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3987,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9599-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3987" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear Delegates!<br><br>These were the words I first heard about half a decade ago as a novice delegate sitting confused in a UNSC committee for the very first time but it was not long before I was fascinated by the quality of debate my fellow delegates brought and since then, there has been no looking back. Nearly 15+ Model UNs later I find myself as the chairperson of the League of Nations in the prestigious Shishukunj MUN 2023.&nbsp;<br><br>Apart from a keen interest in debates and public speaking, I also live under the misconception that I am a poet. I have always loved sciences and mathematics, although that may be put to test next year to sum it all up; I am just someone trying to be saksham in what I do!<br><br>Over my past experiences as a delegate I realised the strength of the UN, of the UNSC, an international body which has the power to bind nations together but the question was: Whether it shall be as successful in the future. To quote Patrick Henry, There is no way of judging the future but by judging from the  past. And judging by the past, there is no better way of ensuring the strength of the UN than to build it up from scratch, from the first letters of the preamble, from 1945!<br><br>It is with these motivations that I welcome you to the prestigious Shishukunj Model UNs 8th iteration, to the newest version of the United Nations Security Council: The League Of Nations. The Committee revolves around the historic agenda of deliberating over the second world war with special emphasis on the future of global institutions. Capturing Nazi warlords and re-working the structure of the UN are some of the exciting matters which await you delegates!<br><br>The Committee revolves around the historic agenda of deliberating over the second world war with special emphasis on the future of global institutions. Capturing and trying Nazi warlords and re-working the structure of the UN are some of the exciting matters which await you delegates!<br><br>I hope those who read this do not hesitate to reach out! See you all in August!&nbsp;<br>Till then: Emerge, Evolve, Elevate.<br><br><strong>Saksham Jain</strong><br><strong>Chairperson</strong><br><strong>The League Of Nations</strong><br>saksham.jain.sjc1839@shishukunj.in<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The League of Nations was the 1st international Initiative to bring together the states for the preservation of global peace and lack of conflict. As laid out in the 4th article of the league's covenant 'The council' is one of the strongest bodies of the league for settlement of international disputes. It was created to meet the need for a global platform for talks between nations after the devastating consequences of world war 1 were realised.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Deliberating over World War II with Emphasis on the Future of Global Institutions</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">At the final season of the council global leaders shall aim to come to teams and adopt&nbsp; an acceptable and peaceful resolution to the world war. They will further be reviewing and amending the institutional design of the league to witness the birth of the United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":2644,"width":150,"height":150,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HqWzBdaFQbtfP2CnZO9TPvT63Td-mvuC/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lon.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2644" style="object-fit:cover;width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>LoN</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3154 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pcij.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>

<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>

<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.6rem">PERMANENT COURT OF INTERNATIONAL JUSTICE</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.2rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.2rem">AGENDA : Defining Legal Jurisdiction and Basis of Prosecution for War Crimes in Wake of the Second World War</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3995,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/dhimmant-sodani-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3995" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br>my name is Dhimant Sodani and it is my esteemed pleasure to serve as the Chairperson of the Permanent Court of International Justice in Shishukunj MUN 2023.<br><br>I am an 11th grader pursuing commerce with applied mathematics. I love MUNing, acting and debating (specially the Arnab Goswami types in which I can shout at the top of my voice). I am a new entrepreneur and a political enthusiast, you can see me gossiping with people about local politics or quarrelling with someone on a national issue. I am a cinephile (bollywood buff), writer and I write poems and verses on love, motivation. I have been quizzing since the past 2 years and have won some important ones too. My MUN journey of the past 5 years has been amazing and has taught me much about the world and society. I would like my delegates to be confident in their approach and connect with the agenda and the committee.<br><br>PCIJ has been introduced for the first time in Shishukunj MUN as a mutually dependent committee along with the League of Nations.<br><br>The agenda of Defining Legal Jurisdiction and Basis of Prosecution for War Crimes in Wake of the Second World War will take you back in the pages of history to the times of World War 2 where you as advocates, representatives or leaders involved in World War 2 will give your opinion on the most brutal incidents of history and will form grounds on which people involved in the war should be prosecuted. I urge the delegates to come up with diplomatic and innovative solutions to solve this global problem to reinstate peace in the world.<br>Looking forward to seeing you in August.<br><br>With Best Wishes<br><strong>Dhimant Sodani<br>Chairperson<br>Permanent Court of International Justice</strong><br>dhimant.sodani.sjc2182@shishukunj.in<strong><br></strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Permanent Court Of International Justice was architectured by the Covenant of the LoN and was the first ever Permanent International Tribunal with General Jurisdiction and was responsible for holding together twentieth century world peace. It is the predecessor to the International Court of Justice, and it laid out all of the groundwork for the ICJ. It was established in 1922 and was dissolved in favour of the ICJ in 1946.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Defining Legal Jurisdiction and Basis of Prosecution for War Crimes in Wake of the Second World War</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The committee is tasked with the responsibility to reframe the structure of International Law by defining legally, various new war crimes by taking account of the events of the second world war and also thereby convicting culprits with regard of said law</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2651,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jSyzTpzsnx47pv7cOPGODVY4T40RNiGU/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pcij.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2651" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>PCIJ</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"47px"} -->
<div style="height:47px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-911 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/press-corps-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.8rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.8rem">PRESS CORPS</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.4rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.4rem">Agenda: Ensuring the Safety of Journalists and Media Persons Worldwide</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.3rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.3rem"><strong>Letter from the Presiding Officials</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4047,"width":444,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9726-2.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-4047" style="width:444px" width="444" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false}} -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br>It gives us immense pleasure to welcome you all to the eighth iteration of the Shishukunj Model United Nations. We, Prutha Pimpalgaonkar, and Saarth Kothari will be serving as the Presiding Officials for Press Corps, a unique and dynamic committee with a lot to offer.<br><br>Prutha is a twelfth grader who is always down to learnwhether it be psychology or something that is out of her forte, like organic chemistryit is her yearning for knowledge that keeps her going. Apart from this, shes just an ordinary girl with an undying love for literature and language. Books are her safe haven, and you can find her screaming about her favourites on her blog at times. She also takes great pride in being a self-taught polyglot, with this skill being primarily driven by wanting to understand K-pop songs without referring to translations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false}} -->
<p>Saarth is a person who is puzzled when it comes to the simplest of things, but extremely decisive in times where the situation is complex. He loves delving into topics such as mythology, sports, or geopolitics, for they give him an instant dopamine boost. Public speaking is one thing which showcases every aspect of his personality and helps him connect with people from different walks of life. In his free time, he can be found either jamming to music on Spotify, or ranting away on his notes app.&nbsp;<br><br>This year, journalists in the International Press will be tasked with something morea debate session, representing various news agencies, and conducting press conferences, to name a fewall as an initiative to make the conference a little more interesting and engaging.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false}} -->
<p>We hope that each and every one of you will be able to kindle a passion for journalism and learn something new, all while taking this as an opportunity to enjoy it to the fullest.<br><br>Thank you, and we look forward to meeting you all!<br><br>Regards,<br><strong>Prutha Pimpalgaonkar and Saarth Kothari<br>Presiding Officials<br>Press Corps<br></strong>prutha.pimpalgaonkar.sjc6973@shishukunj.in and saarth.kothari.sjc2302@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Press Corps plays a vital role in the functioning of an MUN by keeping the delegates updated with the proceedings of all committees. The delegates part of this committee, who will be representing various news agencies, will spend a quarter of the total time debating, while the rest will be spent reporting</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Ensuring the Safety of Journalists and Media Persons Worldwide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The breach of basic human rights are becoming increasingly common in the case of journalists and media persons. Delegates will be deliberating to find solutions to ensure that no journalist or media person is harmed while they perform their duties, both during war and peace times.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2921,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1N8lZW4GeNa8osvUAYH78b3aacLNyympT/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/press-corps.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-2921" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Press Corps</strong></figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior GA]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-aksh-ga/</link>
  <pubDate>Mon, 08 May 2023 14:35:25 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=460</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/ga-bg.jpeg","id":1143,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1143 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/ga-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;text-transform:uppercase">General Assembly</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":4,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"900"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h4 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:900"><br><strong>Letter from the Under Secretary General : General Assembly </strong></h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"stretch"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3636,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9634.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3636" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Dear Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>It is with great pleasure that I welcome all of you to the Shishukunj MUN 2023-24. I will be serving as the USG - General Assembly during this iteration of the SISMUN.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>I find the science behind everything to be very interesting, and so it is without a doubt that I am a PCM student. You can find me procrastinating from procrastinating, while listening to music and reading books of course. I am one of those who dont believe in the so-called Self-Help Books since I believe in the philosophy of going out and getting it done, which is shown by my behavior, as long as there is productivity, anything is permitted.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The General Assembly is one of the six principal organs of the United Nations, and it addresses issues ranging from disarmament to decolonization to human right violations and everything in between. There are 6 main committees under GA, in which all the 193 member states have equal representation, it is the most inclusive organ which works towards achieving world peace and harmony, capturing the essence of what the United Nations truly encapsulates.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>For this iteration, we have 4 committees under the General Assembly - DISEC, UNHCR, UNICEF and Lok Sabha, all of whose agendas have been formed to ensure rich debates and interesting discussions, the agendas going from biochemical weaponry, to security of children, to labor laws.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Reach out to me without any hesitation in case of any doubt/query, I will be more than happy to assist you. Looking forward to meeting all of you and I hope you have a great time!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Regards,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Madhav Dwivedi<br>Under Secretary General : General Assembly<br>Shishukunj MUN Senior Jhalaria 2023</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Committees</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3925,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/aksh-jhalaria-senior-disec/"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/disec-1.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-3925" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>DISEC</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3926,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->

  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-aksh-ecosoc/</link>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1141 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/ecosoc-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem">ECONOMIC AND SOCIAL COUNCIL</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.5rem"></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>Letter from the Under Secretary General : Economic and Social Council</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4027,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9639-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4027" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>I Harbhajan Singh Tuteja, am elated to serve as the Under-Secretary-General of Economic and Social Council of Shishukunj MUN 2023.<br><br>I have opted for commerce with applied mathematics and Entrepreneurship. I am a Business and Finance enthusiast and am on the road to build a career in Portfolio Management. I have been attending MUNs since seventh grade and have gained immensely from them. They have helped me build patience, develop public speaking and excellent researching skills.<br><br>The Economic and Social Council is one of the 6 principal organs of the United Nations. ECOSOC was established under the United Nations Charter as the principal organ to coordinate economic, social, and related work of the 14 UN specialized agencies, functional commissions and five regional commissions. It is the central platform for fostering debate and innovative thinking, forging consensus on ways forward, and coordinating efforts to achieve internationally agreed goals.<br><br>In this Iteration of Shishukunj MUN, we have UNCCPCJ to stop terrorism at source, UNCSW to promote womens right, gender equality and empowerment of women, European Union to discuss the present and future effect of Schengen agreement and UNECA to deliberate upon the Impact of Foreign countries on the Social and Economic Scenario in Africa.<br><br>Feel free to contact me in case of any and every query. Looking forward to making this an experience worth remembering!<br><br>Regards,<br><strong>Harbhajan Singh Tuteja&nbsp;<br>Under-Secretary-General : Economic and Social Council</strong><br><strong>Shishukunj MUN Senior&nbsp;Jhalaria&nbsp;2023</strong><br>harbhajan.tuteja.sjc2288@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Committees</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"25%"} -->

<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior SPECIALIZED AGENCIES]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-aksh-specialized-agencies/</link>
  <pubDate>Mon, 08 May 2023 14:37:39 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=468</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/specialised-agencies-bg.jpeg","id":1145,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1145 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/specialised-agencies-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem">SPECIALIZED AGENCIES</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.5rem"></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2rem"><strong>Letter from the Under Secretary General : Specialized Agencies</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4024,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9632-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4024" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br>With immense pleasure, I, Kanav Bansal, welcome you to the Shishukunj MUN 2023. I'm elated to serve as the USG- Specialised Agencies as well as the Crisis Director of this iteration of the Shishukunj MUN.<br>I am currently a 12<sup>th</sup> grader studying PCM, which showcases my determination and risk-taking attributes. I am a sports enthusiast and you can find me playing any sport(usually ending up in an injury). I have a knack for coming up with amusing and witty dad jokes.<br>I have been MUNing since 6th grade(that 11y/o boy would be proud seeing me here) and they have taught me a lot about World Politics and Crisis Management. I have always had a keen interest in the Specialised agencies.<br><br>International organisations that operate independently and collaborate with the UN make up the UN specialised agencies. Through negotiations, all were brought into a relationship with the UN. Some were around before World War One, some of them had ties to the League of Nations. The UN and other entities were both virtually simultaneously founded. To address new demands, the UN formed others.<br><br>This year we have 3 spellbinding committees under the Specialised Agencies- LoN, PCIJ and an AdHoc. The LoN and the PCIJ are mutually depended committees, which means both committees will operate concurrently and actions taken by one committee would definitely affect the other. As for the AdHoc, well lets wait till the conference. I'll make sure that as delegates, you get the most out of this conference and leave with more knowledge on diplomacy and decision making.<br><br>Feel free to reach out to me in case of any doubt/query, I will be happy to assist you. Looking forward to meeting all of you and I hope you have a great time!<br><br>Regards,<br><br><strong>Kanav Bansal<br>Under-Secretary-General: Specialised Agencies and Crisis Director</strong><br>kanav.bansal.sjc2355@shishukunj.in<br><br><br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Committees</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3919,"aspectRatio":"1","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/jhalaria-aksh-lon/"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/lon-2.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-3919" style="aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>LoN</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3912,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/jhalaria-aksh-permanent-court-of-international-justice/"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/pcij.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-3912" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>PCIJ</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3915,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/ad-hoc-edited.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3915" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Ad-Hoc</strong></figcaption></figure>

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">DISARMAMENT AND INTERNATIONAL SECURITY COUNCIL</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>educing <strong>T</strong>errorism by <strong>E</strong>liminating <strong>F</strong>unding, <strong>M</strong>anufacturing and <strong>T</strong>rade of <strong>I</strong>llicit <strong>W</strong>eapons</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3585,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0098.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3585" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Dear Delegates,&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Namaste</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I, Avani Shrivastava, will be serving as your chairperson of the first committee of the United Nations General Assembly, the Disarmament and International Security Committee. It is my utmost honor to welcome all of you to the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus Model United Nations!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am a 10th grader and wish to pursue law as a career. I particularly enjoy reading, debating, and sports, especially cricket and football. I have been a part of MUNs for the past 3 years, and they have had a great impact on me. It has molded my personality to a great extent and inculcated qualities like diplomacy, patience, research, analytical thinking, public speaking, and interpersonal skills as well. I hope each delegate gathers their share of learning through the conference, which is essential for a dynamic personality.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am absolutely thrilled to serve as your chairperson for this MUN. I expect all delegates to have deep and thorough research of their portfolios, deliberate upon the key sub-topics and all other pressing issues revolving around the agenda, and use the salient skills of diplomacy and negotiation to come up with new, creative as well as practical solutions. I look forward to this committee being an informative, fun, and engaging learning experience for each delegate.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am always open to questions and problems. As your chairperson, I am open to any confusion you might face and want each delegate to reach out to me for any matter concerning them.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I truly cannot wait to meet you all in person soon!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">All the best!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Avani Shrivastava&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Chairperson&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">The Disarmament and International Security Committee</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The Disarmament and International Security Committee (DISEC) is one of the six main committees of the United Nations General Assembly. DISEC focuses on addressing global issues related to disarmament, arms control, and international security. It provides a platform for member states to engage in dialogue, negotiate agreements, and develop strategies to promote peace and security worldwide. DISEC's agenda includes topics such as nuclear disarmament, non-proliferation of weapons, prevention of armed conflicts, and the regulation of conventional arms trade. Through its discussions and resolutions, DISEC contributes to fostering stability, reducing tensions, and building a safer world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda</strong> : <strong>Reducing Terrorism by Eliminating Funding, Manufacturing and Trade of Illicit Weapons</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Terrorism still poses a serious danger to international peace and security and undermines the UN's core principles. The unauthorized trade in firearms is one of the censorious factors that support and sustain terrorism. Our agenda for this committee is Reducing Terrorism by Eliminating Funding, Manufacturing, and Trade of Illicit Weapons. In simple words, the aim of the committee is to reduce the number of weapons in circulation and make it harder for terrorists to carry out their attacks. The core causes of terrorism, such as poverty, political unrest, and social injustice, must also be confronted. Reducing Terrorism by Eliminating Funding, Manufacturing, and Trade of Illicit Weapons is the committee's main agenda, and the committee's goal is to regulate the accessibility of firearms and make it harder for terrorists to carry out their atrocities</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1027,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/disec_study_guide-2.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/disec-1983440656-e1683781553821.webp?w=214" alt="" class="wp-image-1027" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DFK2jnvO4Nr9C7u3ntcgPMsc64dNkAMhAAwQqEA3dOk/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>
