<item>
  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNCSocD]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-uncsocd/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:46:20 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=604</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/uncsocd.jpg","id":980,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-980" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/uncsocd.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"53px"} -->
<div style="height:53px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONs COMMISSION FOR SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT 1</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>I</strong>mplementation of <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>D</strong>evelopment <strong>G</strong>oal <strong>4</strong>- <strong>E</strong>ducation</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3615,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0110.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3615" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Dear Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I hope this letter finds you in the pink of your health. I am honored to serve as the Chairperson of the United Nations Commission for Social Development (UNCSocD) for this very first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus MUN 2023.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Allow me to introduce myself. My name is Aarna Anjali Sharma, and I am currently in the tenth grade. I have been participating in MUN conferences for the past 5 years, as I find them to be an experience that has consistently enriched my understanding of global affairs and fostered my passion for international relations. In my leisure time, I find solace in the world of books, swimming, and writing.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The UNCSocD is a dynamic committee entrusted with the responsibility of addressing social development challenges and promoting sustainable solutions. For this session, our central focus will be on implementing Sustainable Development Goal 4 (SDG 4), which aims to ensure inclusive and equitable quality education for all.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">SDG 4 holds tremendous significance as it lays the foundation for achieving several other Sustainable Development Goals.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I encourage each of you to come prepared with thoughtful insights, creative solutions, and a willingness to engage in constructive debate. Please do not hesitate to reach out to me if you have any questions, concerns, or ideas regarding the committee's agenda or the conference itself. I am here to support and guide you throughout the proceedings.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am truly looking forward to meeting each one of you and embarking on this journey of stimulating debates and discussions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I wish you the best in your preparations and look forward to a fruitful conference!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Sincerely,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Aarna Anjali Sharma</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Chairperson United Nations Commission for Social Development (UNCSocD)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Commission for Social Development (UNCSocD) is a body dedicated to addressing global social development challenges. It serves as a platform for member states to discuss and formulate policies aimed at promoting social progress, reducing poverty, and improving the well-being of all individuals. The UNCSocD focuses on issues such as poverty eradication, employment generation, social integration, and sustainable development. It plays a crucial role in fostering international cooperation, sharing best practices, and coordinating efforts to create a more inclusive and equitable world for all.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Implementation of Sustainable Development Goal 4- Education</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda for this committee focuses on implementing Sustainable Development Goal 4, Ensuring inclusive and equitable quality education'. This crucial goal aims to ensure inclusive and equitable education for all, promote lifelong learning opportunities, and foster global literacy. The committee will delve into discussions on strategies to enhance educational access, improve educational infrastructure, and develop inclusive educational policies. Delegates will explore innovative solutions to address the challenges of educational inequality, promote education for sustainable development, and strengthen the role of education in achieving overall sustainable development.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":5267,"width":"140px","height":"120px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/uncsocd1.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/csocd.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-5267" style="object-fit:cover;width:140px;height:120px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7333333333333333","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"thumbnail","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-thumbnail is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17JoyPpHSkyUg0HoHtGOeS9C0RAQyrEHgfeW5M3Q_hKY/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp?w=97" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="aspect-ratio:0.7333333333333333;object-fit:cover;width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior UNCSW]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-uncsw/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:49:21 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=605</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/uncsw-bg.png","id":914,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-914 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/uncsw-bg.png)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem">UNITED NATIONS COMMISSION ON THE STATUS OF WOMEN</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.3rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.3rem">Agenda: Adopting Measures to Prevent Chauvinist Sentiments and Ferity Against Women</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Co Chairpersons</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4050,"width":460,"height":300,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9613-1-edited-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4050" style="object-fit:cover" width="460" height="300" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear Delegates&nbsp;<br>Namaste! We, Aishwarya Bansal and Satvik Phalswal, Co-Chairpersons of UNCSW are tremendously excited to welcome you to the Shishukunj Model United Nations 2023.&nbsp; It is our distinct honor to welcome you to this prestigious conference. We hope this conference will give you new points of outlook towards significant world issues and is an improving and edifying experience.&nbsp;<br><br>I, Aishwarya Bansal, am a 12th-grader commerce student. I have been MUNing for the past five years and each conference I have attended has assisted me in developing as an individual. My hobbies include reading and listening to music, though these could easily pass on as things I like to do while procrastinating. I am also an art enthusiast and enjoy doing things like sketching and painting that spark my inner creative self. I also love to travel and explore new places.<br>&nbsp;<br>I, Satvik Phalswal, am currently in grade XI (PCM with CS) and this is my third year of association with Model United Nation conferences. I have been the Senior Vice-Captain for the Dhyanchand house. My hobbies include activities that give me an adrenaline boost, mountain biking, participating in high endurance activities like marathons and long-distance cycling, reading, and gaining knowledge on global affairs. In the future, I aspire to be a 9 Paratroopers Regiment, Special Forces Commando in the Indian Army.&nbsp;<br><br>We believe that MUNs are a fascinating platform for bringing together science and international relations because they challenge students to consider scientific solutions to real-world issues and expose them to the current world.<br>UNCSW is one of the most important organs of the UN and its main aim is to help women build a better life and society. It is a subsidiary body of the UN WOMEN and aims mainly at promoting gender equality and empowerment of women. This year's agenda is Adopting Measures to Prevent Chauvinist Sentiments and Ferity Against Women. We will discuss and debate the specifics of the problem, the various issues, and find solutions for the same. We hope we will be able to make this MUN&nbsp; a memorable learning experience for you all. We will be more than happy to answer your questions before, during, and after the conference.&nbsp;<br><br>Looking forward to meeting you all!<br><br>Regards,<br><strong>Aishwarya Bansal &amp; Satvik Phalswal<br>Co - Chairpersons<br>United Nations Commission on the Status of Women</strong><br>aishwarya.bansal.sjc2280@shishukunj.in and satvik.phalswal.sjc6641@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The United Nations Commission on the Status of Women is a subsidiary working body of UN WOMEN. It is exclusively dedicated to promote gender equality and the empowerment of women. It promotes womens rights, documents the reality of their lives and shapes global standards for their empowerment.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Adopting Measures to Prevent Chauvinist Sentiments and Ferity Against Women</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Women worldwide face the effects of the misogynistic sentiments that prevail. Their rights are violated and numerous women are victims of violence and ill treatment. Horrendous practices such as femicide, female genital mutilation, domestic violence, etc make their life difficult. The delegates would be discussing these problems in depth and deliberating on the measures that can be adopted to curb such practices.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2639,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PEpRHWSoKKVRiCdU1MxKwqfORf9tBdAE/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/uncsw.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2639" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNCSW</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>

  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/nato-1.jpg","id":958,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-958" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/nato-1.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"53px"} -->
<div style="height:53px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>D</strong>iscussing <strong>NATOs</strong> <strong>I</strong>nfluence on the <strong>A</strong>sia-<strong>P</strong>acific <strong>R</strong>egion</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"152px"} -->
<div style="height:152px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3620,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0078.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3620" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Dear Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am Manya Shah and it is my privilege to welcome you all to the North Atlantic Treaty Organization on behalf of the entire bureau. I will be serving as your chairperson for this committee. NATO will be a specialized crisis committee where instant problems and crises will intensify the agenda at hand.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am a 10th grader exploring the possibilities the world has to offer with a trillion songs in my head to keep me alive. Youll usually find me with my nose buried in a book or a blanket, or if youre lucky, youll catch me staring at the mirror with my ghungroos on, expressing my emotions through Kathak.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I started my MUNing in 2019 by assisting the staff as a logistic member. I owe becoming a chairperson to that 2019 committee which ignited the fire of diplomacy in me. MUNs have helped shape my personality in terms of public speaking, cooperation and confidence.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I cannot express my enthusiasm for chairing NATO and expect the same to make the committee even more fun. Crisis committees follow a different procedure than regular committees. They require intense research and fast thinking. So, keep your weapons for the committee sessions ready (metaphorically, of course, we do NOT want a war).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Prepare well for discussions and debates that you will enjoy thoroughly.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I check my emails regularly and assure you that your doubts will not go unanswered. Do not hesitate to reach out to me and I will be more than happy to answer your doubts and listen to you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Words fall short to welcome you all to NATO this year.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Eager to meet you all soon!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Warm Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Manya Shah</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Chairperson</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">NATO</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">NATO, the North Atlantic Treaty Organization, is an intergovernmental military alliance established for collective defense and security cooperation among its member states. Comprising 30 countries, NATO aims to safeguard the freedom and security of its members through political consultations, military preparedness, and cooperative security measures. It serves as a platform for member states to address shared security challenges, promote stability in the Euro-Atlantic region, and foster transatlantic cooperation. NATO's core principles include collective defense, crisis management, and partnership engagement, making it a vital pillar of international security and defense cooperation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Discussing NATOs Influence on the Asia-Pacific Region</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda of this committee, "NATOs increasing influence in the Asia-Pacific," is undeniably an important topic. It explores areas of debate and issues capable of altering foreign relations, world politics, and security. As tensions in the South China Sea build up and relations with Russia become increasingly adverse due to the Russo-Ukraine war, everything from trade and commerce to defence and security is getting affected. To maintain peace and balance of power on the globe, discussing NATO's influence in the Asia-Pacific, the integration of its allies, and the security measures to be taken must be deliberated over, and that is what this committee aims at through this MUN.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":1073,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/nato-study-guide-shishukunj-mun-2023.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/nato-1.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-1073" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"76px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/10FJEDaEQBK1WlrxPGTwoz_VAJqG229tX/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:76px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior DISEC]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-disec/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:52:18 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=617</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/disec-bg.png","id":845,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-845 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/disec-bg.png)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.6rem">DISARMAMENT AND INTERNATIONAL SECURITY COMMITTEE</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.4rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.4rem">Agenda: Controlling Weapons of Mass Destruction With Emphasis On Bio Chemical Weapons</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3945,"width":200,"height":300,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9702-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3945" style="width:200px;height:300px" width="200" height="300" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br><br>It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you to the 8th edition of the Shishukunj Model United Nations. I, Arnav Shrivastav, am honoured to serve as the chairperson of the Disarmament and International Security Committee (DISEC).<br><br>I'm a 12th grader studying commerce with applied mathematics with the view of pursuing CA and CFA in the future. I have this weird inclination of trying to be every possible juniors favourite senior. I am meticulous and coherent, at least thats what my friends say. I consider myself as a congenial person and am sometimes narcissistic too. I am a bit passionate about music, I play guitar and love to listen to various genres of music. I love to travel, but road trips are a different gravy for me. MUNs have always been fun and a great learning experience for me since I was a 7th grader, I have learned a lot from them and would never regret participating in any one of them. DISEC is one of the committees I absolutely love and am very excited to chair.<br><br>This year DISEC's agenda will be 'Controlling Weapons of mass destruction with emphasis on biochemical weaponry'. The use of biochemical weaponry is one of the biggest security threats to the world, this committee will focus on disarmament of both these categories of weapons with respect to both state and non state actors.<br><br>I'll make sure that as delegates you'll make the most out of this committee and leave with more knowledge on world politics and diplomacy.<br>Looking forward to meeting you all soon and I hope you all have fun.&nbsp;<br>Feel free to contact me in case of any queries/doubts.<br><br>Regards&nbsp;<strong><br>Arnav Shrivastav<br>Chairperson</strong><br><strong>Disarmament and International Security Committee</strong><br><a href="mailto:arnav.shrivastav.sjc2457@shishukunj.in">arnav.shrivastav.sjc2457@shishukunj.in</a><br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">DISEC was created as the first of the main committees in the General Assembly when the UN charter was signed. DISEC addresses and deals with issues related to disarmament and international security. It considers all disarmament and international security matters within the scope of the charter or relating to the powers and functions of any other organ of the United Nations</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Controlling Weapons of Mass Destruction With Emphasis On Bio Chemical Weapons</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The use of biochemical weaponry is one of the biggest security threats to the world. The cost of these weapons is relatively very less when compared to nuclear weapons which makes it easier to replace nuclear weapons. This committee will focus on disarmament of these weapons with respect to both state as well as non state actors. Delegates will be required to discuss threats, loopholes in conventions, possibility of a warfare, its viability on International peace and find potential solutions for the same.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"wide","id":4641,"width":150,"height":150,"scale":"contain","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom","className":"is-style-default"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large is-resized is-style-default"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1N0PhFRzyrYvc_WqUIONu76QFDtwSVxfP/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/disec-2.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-4641" style="object-fit:contain;width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>DISEC</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","fontSize":"2.9rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.9rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS ENVIRONMENT PROGRAMME 1</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>educing the <strong>N</strong>egative <strong>I</strong>mpact of <strong>P</strong>lastic on the <strong>E</strong>nvironment</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"222px"} -->
<div style="height:222px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3596,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0090.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3596" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">Dear Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">Namaste</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">I, Asmi Chaudhary, will be serving as your chairperson for the United Nations Environment Programme. I am thrilled to welcome you to the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus Model United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">I, Asmi Chaudhary, am an eleventh-grader studying commerce with mathematics. I wish to pursue a career in economics and psychology. I enjoy dancing, writing and reading all kinds of novels. I have been participating in MUNs since I was in seventh grade and the journey so far has taught me a plethora of 21st-century skills. As an avid MUNer, I have learned diplomacy, consensus-building, communication, confidence, and research skills. I sincerely hope that through this experience, you get to develop all these skills as well.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">I am extremely excited and honored to serve as your chairperson for this MUN. I expect each delegate to be thorough with their research, dive into the various sub-topics revolving around the agenda, and after careful deliberation of the agenda, negotiate with other delegates to form a consensus and come up with innovative solutions. I want the committee to be engaging, informative, and fun for all delegates, and thus participation is expected from everybody, regardless of the experience one has.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">I am here to guide you through the entire conference and help you build essential skills to vamp up your personality.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">Please feel free to reach out to us whenever you feel the need to.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">We look forward to meeting all of you in person.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.5"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="line-height:1.5">All the best!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Asmi Choudhary</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Chairperson</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">United Nations Development Programme</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0"><br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) is the leading global authority on environmental issues. It works to promote sustainable development, protect the environment, and address pressing challenges such as climate change, biodiversity loss, and pollution. UNEP collaborates with governments, organizations, and communities to develop policies, raise awareness, and implement solutions for environmental conservation. Through its programs and initiatives, UNEP plays a crucial role in fostering international cooperation, driving policy changes, and promoting sustainable practices to ensure a healthy and resilient planet for present and future generations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Reducing the Negative Impact of Plastic on the Environment</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda for UNEP is "Reducing the Negative Effects of Plastic on the Environment". Plastic is the most widely used commodity in the world and is used in the production of practically everything. But the problem with this magic material is that it is non-degradable. It only accumulates in huge heaps and harms all spheres of the ecosystem: the ocean, land, forests, and biodiversity. It kills innocent animals and depletes the soil's quality. Humans also suffer from the negative effects of plastic, as it directly affects the livelihoods of millions of people. Such problems are a hindrance to achieving the sustainable development goals of proper production and consumption, climate change, and life on water and land. The world needs effective solutions that are formed on a global level and implemented with international cooperation to curb this crisis.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1071,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/unep-1.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/enep-1.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1071" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DFK2jnvO4Nr9C7u3ntcgPMsc64dNkAMhAAwQqEA3dOk/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-898 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unicef-bg.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize","fontSize":"2.7rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.7rem;text-transform:capitalize">UNITED NATION INTERNATIONAL CHILDREN'S EMERGENCY FUND</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.5rem">Agenda: Addressing the Needs and Security of Children with Emphasis on Conflict Zones</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3971,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9621-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3971" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Namaste,&nbsp;<br>It gives me immense pleasure and pride to welcome you to the Shishukunj MUN 2023. I am Shreya Vyas ,I will be serving as the Chairperson for the United Nations International Children's Emergency Fund ( UNICEF ).<br><br>I am an eleventh grader studying PCM with the view of becoming an engineer. I started doing MUNs in 6th grade and I've fallen in love with all elements of it and its journey. I am an ambivert and I love meeting new people.&nbsp; The series Mentalist is my absolute love. I am the biggest chatterbox and I can talk about everything endlessly. I love listening to music.&nbsp;<br><br>Seeing children play brings a smile to our faces and UNICEF works for the smiles on those children's faces. UNICEF's goal is to ensure that no child is left behind. The agenda of UNICEF this year in Shishukunj MUN is ' Addressing the needs and security of children with emphasis on developing countries '. Children all over the world face numerous problems ranging from lack of resources to abuse as well as exploitation.The committee shall be focusing on improving the existing laws made for children and find solutions for the loopholes present in the system.<br><br>I hope that this committee provides a learning opportunity for all of you and helps you get a better understanding of world politics and diplomacy . Please do not hesitate to reach out to me for any doubts.<br><br>Thank you and see you all soon!<br><br>Regards,&nbsp;<br><strong>Shreya Vyas<br>Chairperson&nbsp;<br><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>United Nations International Children's Emergency Fund</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong><br>shreya.vyas.sjc2200@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">UNICEF was adopted by the United Nations General Assembly in 1989 to protect children's rights, to help them achieve their basic needs and to ensure that no child is left behind. It works in over 190 countries and territories to safeguard childrens lives, rights and helps them achieve their full potential.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Addressing the Needs and Security of Children with Emphasis on Conflict Zones</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The development of children requires a safe environment along with provision of basic amenities such as education, healthcare, sanitation etc.&nbsp;Children all over the world face several challenges due to exploitation, abuse and lack of resources that hinders their physical and psychological development. The committee aims to strengthen existing laws and establish suitable institutions to aid the situation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"wide","id":4630,"width":150,"height":150,"scale":"contain","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sQQ8oFIUoel6PQIbH9LA7mL8A7viEf1e/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unicef-final.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-4630" style="object-fit:contain;width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNICEF</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior EU]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-eu/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:56:48 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=631</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/eu-bg.png","id":888,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-888 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/eu-bg.png)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:3rem">EUROPEAN UNION</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.3rem">Agenda: Discussion on the Schengen Agreement with emphasis on Trade Policies and Refugee Regulations</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3967,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9697-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3967" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Greetings to all delegates! I am Akarsha Garg, and I will be serving as the Chairperson of the European Union in Shishukunj MUN 23.&nbsp;<br><br>Reading, interacting with people and learning new things are some of my favorite hobbies, MUNing fits right into the list of things I love and it has been a totally splendid journey so far, which is to continue for times to come. Today, Ive been given the opportunity to chair this unique and strong organization we know as the EU.&nbsp;<br><br>We all are well aware that this is no ordinary committee, it is much more than a partnership between 27 nations within Europe, it has extraordinary aims and values which drive it towards becoming more successful than it already is. Europe is a powerful continent, and anything that happens here, affects the whole world. And hence the agenda well be discussing is not simply a problem within Europe, it involves and has effects on nations all around the world. It is comprehensive, it has to be seen from various perspectives and understood thoroughly&nbsp; if it has to be solved.&nbsp;<br><br>What we expect from the delegates is extensive research, discussion and debate, on every aspect of the problem in hand, think about its causes as well as its impacts and come up with original and creative solutions in order to solve it.&nbsp;<br>Hoping to see vital and mindful discussions!<br><br>Regards,<br><strong>Akarsha Garg<br>Chairperson<br>European Union</strong><br>akarsha.garg.sjc1891@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Established on November 1, 1993 in Netherlands, the European Union is a unique and successful partnership between the 27 member states it has today. The members laid its foundation to promote unity and interdependence, a goal which this organization has successfully been achieving. The EU legislation, which believes in pooling of sovereignty on a multitude of sectors, works together through common institutions to make policies and promote their interests</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Discussion on the Schengen Agreement with special emphasis on Trade Policies and Refugee Regulations</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The Schengen Agreement was signed in 1985 by 5 countries in Luxembourg. Today, it has a total of 28 countries as a part of it, 24 of which are EU nations and 4 are non- EU nations. The agreement was signed with the purpose of abolishment of national borders for free and easy movement of people, and it remains one of the biggest areas with limited to no border control. Naturally, this area has its own problems. The problem with refugees is that there exist conflicting ideologies of member states about refugees, and hence a consensus about refugee regulations is a bit of a problem. High numbers of immigration affects the government as well as the citizens, and the danger of illegal activities persists. Talking about trade, free trade is what needs to be discussed and debated upon. How much trade should be regulated(internally as well as externally), threats like international crime, etc are all that are included under trade. There also exist more challenges which need to be solved, like situation on borders, the impacts of policies, security changes, etc.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2637,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SyjZ541Gk-aDZJ_akAerQk4mpQoOn1Wr/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/eu.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-2637" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>EU</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>
