<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior UNECA]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-uneca/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:58:47 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=635</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/uneca.jpeg","id":3145,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3145 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/uneca.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem">UNITED NATIONS ECONOMIC COMMISSION FOR AFRICA</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.4rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.4rem">Agenda: Impact of Foreign countries on the Social and Economic Scenario in Africa</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3956,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/saanvi-shrimalli-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3956" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br>I, Sanvi Shrimali, feel honored to welcome you to the Shishukunj MUN 2023 as the Chairperson of United Nations Economic Commission of Africa.&nbsp;<br><br>Apart from carefully curating Spotify playlists dedicated to Taylor Swift (no. 1 swiftie here) and covering all of Netflix, Im an ardent reader with a sense of humor not to be missed (at least according to my friends). Im a class 11 science student aiming for a career in engineering. Ive been a part of several MUNs and I hope they give you all the same exposure and confidence that they have given me.<br><br>The agenda for our committee is the Impact of Foreign countries on the Social and Economic Scenario in Africa. With our world becoming a global village, all nations face direct or indirect influence from each other. UNECA endeavors to hold discussions and debates regarding all aspects of impacts of other nations on Africa which will finally lead to the re-evaluation of current policies to improve Africas economic situation.&nbsp;<br>I hope that all of you have an enriching experience and reach fruitful conclusions.<br><br>In case of any questions, please feel free to contact me.&nbsp;<br>Thank you and cant wait to meet you all!<br><br>Warmest Regards,<br><strong>Sanvi Shrimali<br>Chairperson<br>United Nations Economic Commission for Africa</strong><br>sanvi.shrimali.sjc2094@shishukunj.in<br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Established in 1958, UNECA is one of the UNs five regional commissions.&nbsp; It aims to develop the economic and social stance of its member States, reinforce intra regional integration and promote&nbsp; international cooperation for the common goal of amelioration of Africa</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Impact of Foreign countries on the Social and Economic Scenario in Africa</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The committee aims to be a platform for the discussion and debate of the impact endured by Africa at the hands of foreign countries - positive and negative . It plans to refine the existing mandates and rules via mutual team effort to eradicate exploitation , financial gap and improve the economy of Africa .</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2642,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qTI2QStivcYwnNSUX49TpGU0ZMmSaXbF/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/uneca.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-2642" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNECA</strong></figcaption></figure>

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus WHO]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-who/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 09:58:34 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=636</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/who-e1687365163621.jpg","id":2836,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2836" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/who-e1687365163621.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"150px","height":"150px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="object-fit:cover;width:150px;height:150px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><span style="font-size: 28.8px"><b>AGEN</b></span><strong>DA:</strong> <strong>A</strong>chieving <strong>U</strong>niversal <strong>H</strong>ealthcare</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Letter From The Chairpersons</strong> </h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":4987,"width":"400px","height":"290px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/img_2371.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-4987" style="object-fit:cover;width:400px;height:290px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left has-background-color has-text-color">Dear delegates,<br><br>We, Khayal Garg and Nikunj Khandelwal, have the distinct privilege of serving as the co-chairpersons for the World Health Organisation. It is with utmost honor that we welcome each of you to the inaugural edition of the Shishukunj North Campus MUN!<br><br>I am Khayal Garg, an 11th-grade student with a profound interest in economics and aspire to pursue a career in management. I am passionate about public speaking, debating, playing the piano, and, of course, MUNing.<br><br>I, Nikunj Khandelwal, am a 10th grader and I hope to pursue science the very next year as a subject. As hobbies, I enjoy going to the gym, taking part in political debates and at times, playing the guitar.<br><br>The enthusiasm and excitement we feel as co-chairs of WHO this year is simply unmatched. The agenda for this year's conference, 'Achieving Universal Healthcare,' focuses on addressing the challenges faced by individuals worldwide in accessing equitable and comprehensive primary healthcare services while seeking viable solutions.<br><br>As co-chairs, we expect each one of you to delve deeply into each subtopic and conduct thorough research so that you are delegating not at a model, but at an actual UN conference. We are fully committed to fostering an interactive and engaging committee while also ensuring that this experience is both enlightening and enjoyable for all delegates. Should any questions, concerns, or doubts arise, please do not hesitate to reach out to us .<br>We are wholeheartedly looking forward to the conference and meeting all of you.<br><br><strong>Warm Regards,</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:image {"id":3289,"width":"157px","height":"81px","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/who-e1687718008485.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3289" style="width:157px;height:81px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":3292,"width":"169px","height":"82px","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/who-2-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3292" style="width:169px;height:82px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color"><strong><br>Khayal Garg and Nikunj Khandelwal<br>Chairpersons </strong><br><strong>World Health Organisation</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The World Health Organization (WHO) is a specialized agency of the United Nations, focusing on global public health. Its primary objective is to promote health, prevent diseases, and provide universal access to healthcare services. WHO coordinates international efforts in disease surveillance, response to health emergencies, and the development of health policies and guidelines. It works with governments, health professionals, and partners to combat major health challenges, such as infectious diseases, non-communicable diseases, and health inequalities. WHO plays a critical role in protecting and improving the health of populations worldwide.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda: <strong>Achieving Universal Healthcare</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda, Achieving Universal Healthcare, aims to address the need for healthcare access and coverage for all individuals, regardless of their socio-economic background. The agenda is closely aligned with the 3rd SDG and seeks to explore sustainable strategies to ensure affordable and quality healthcare services, promote preventive care, enhance healthcare infrastructure, address healthcare disparities, and strengthen healthcare systems globally. Delegates would be expected to discuss unique solutions, collaborative partnerships, and policy frameworks to overcome the barriers and achieve equitable healthcare for all, thus improving public health outcomes and fostering global well-being.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1069,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/who_study_guide-2.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/who-1.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-1069" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DFK2jnvO4Nr9C7u3ntcgPMsc64dNkAMhAAwQqEA3dOk/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior Lok Sabha]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-lok-sabha/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 10:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=643</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lok-sabha.jpeg","id":3157,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":40,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-40 has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3157 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lok-sabha.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:3rem">LOK SABHA</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.3rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-size:1.3rem">Agenda: Discussion on the Exploitation of Labour Workers and Patching The Loopholes in Modern&nbsp;Labor&nbsp;Laws</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3949,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9709-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3949" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>I, Pradhyot Upadhyay, feel extremely delighted and honoured to welcome you all to the Lok Sabha committee of the Shishukunj Model United Nations, 2023.<br><br>I am a science student studying in 11th standard, with hopes of joining the National Defence Academy after school. I am a sports enthusiast, and I especially watch football, tennis and basketball. I love doing MUNs and have been doing them for quite a lot of time, particularly due to my interest in geography and geopolitics.<br><br>I personally believe that Lok Sabha is a unique committee and stands out from all the other committees in any MUN. It focuses on discussing issues that us as Indians can easily relate to. Lok Sabha is the House of the People, the lower house of the parliament of the worlds largest democracy.<br><br>In my experience, I have seen that communication and research go hand in hand. To be a successful delegate, it is important to be well prepared and have confidence in your research, along with being able to stay confident while making your point. This committee will provide a platform for negotiations and debates, along with brilliant and innovative solutions for the real world.<br><br>Feel free to contact us regarding any issues or doubts.&nbsp;<br><br>We wish you best of luck for the coming conference. Good luck and Godspeed.&nbsp;<br><br>Thank you!<br><br>Regards,<br><strong>Pradhyot Upadhyay<br>Chairperson<br>Lok Sabha</strong><br>pradhyot.upadhyay.sjc2121@shishukunj.in<strong><br></strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Lok Sabha, the House of the People, came into being after Indias independence to discuss government policies,amendments and to discuss other issues and solutions throughout India. It is the lower house of the Indian Parliament and has a fair representation of all the states and sections of the society to safeguard the world's largest democracy.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Discussion on the Exploitation of Labour Workers and Patching The Loopholes in Modern&nbsp;Labor&nbsp;Laws<br></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The committee aims to solve the problems of labourers and bring in notice the current loopholes in the modern labour laws to prevent labourers from being exploited . The committee also aims to solve issues several other issues of labourers like child labour, discrimination amongst labourers, occupational hazards faced&nbsp;by&nbsp;workers&nbsp;etc.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2630,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ojmVvYdje8LZkv3LSxX5O9B1M4Yxori0/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lok-sabha.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2630" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Lok Sabha</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>
  <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-80 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1901" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/world-bank-4-629204965-e1684925015384.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->

<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>

<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">WORLD BANK</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>D</strong>iscussing the <strong>N</strong>eed for a <strong>N</strong>ew <strong>G</strong>lobal <strong>R</strong>eserve <strong>C</strong>urrency with <strong>S</strong>pecial <strong>E</strong>mphasis on <strong>C</strong>ryptocurrency</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":5007,"width":"204px","height":"300px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/img_2521-1.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-5007" style="object-fit:cover;width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"},"dimensions":{"minHeight":""}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Dear Delegates</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">It gives me immense pleasure and privilege to welcome you to the Shishukunj North Campus MUN 2023. I, Arham Bandi, am honored to serve as the Chairperson of the World Bank.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am an eleventh grader with a special interest in economics. I have been participating in MUNs for the past five years. I always look forward to new experiences and hope that this MUN serves as a memorable one for all delegates. I will try my very best to ensure that each delegate becomes even more confident as an individual and, most importantly, has something that they have learned from.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The World Banks mission is to end extreme poverty and promote shared prosperity in a sustainable way. This year, the agenda is "Discussing the Need for a New Global Reserve Currency with Special Emphasis on Cryptocurrency". We will be diving into the specifics of the problem, discussing and debating the various issues, and finding solutions for them. We will make sure that the conference is a memorable experience for all the delegates. Feel free to contact us for any queries or assistance you might need.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">We look forward to meeting you all soon.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4521,"width":"100px","height":"101px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/world-bank.png?w=178" alt="" class="wp-image-4521" style="width:100px;height:101px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700">Thank you!<br>Arham Bandi<br>Chairperson of the World Bank</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The World Bank is an international financial institution focused on reducing poverty and promoting economic development. Comprised of two entities, the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development (IBRD) and the International Development Association (IDA), it provides financial resources, technical expertise, and policy advice to low- and middle-income countries. The World Bank supports projects and programs in areas such as infrastructure, education, healthcare, and environmental sustainability. Additionally, it conducts research and analysis to inform policymaking and foster global development cooperation. The World Bank plays a crucial role in advancing sustainable and inclusive growth worldwide.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Discussing the need for a New Global Reserve Currency with special emphasis on Cryptocurrency</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda of this years World Bank committee is 'Discussing the Need for a New Global Reserve Currency with Special Emphasis on Cryptocurrency." The agenda provides information about the problems of the current reserve, the dominance and misuse of traditional reserves in the international market and how cryptocurrencies and new digital currencies can offer some advantages in terms of stability, security and neutrality. After the Second World War, the dominance of the dollar in the International markets became prominent. With a changing geopolitical landscape and losing confidence in the US Dollar, the new global economy asks for a more stable and decentralized currency. The aim of the committee is to discuss and develop a new reserve currency along with an international monetary and exchange rate system that incorporates this new currency as a reserve asset.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":5472,"width":"100px","height":"100px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/world-bank-study-guide.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/world_bank-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="wp-image-5472" style="object-fit:cover;width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7333333333333333","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"thumbnail","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS SECURITY COUNCIL</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>A</strong>ddressing <strong>T</strong>he <strong>S</strong>outh <strong>C</strong>hina <strong>S</strong>ea <strong>C</strong>onflict</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"152px"} -->
<div style="height:152px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3587,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0080.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3587" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Greetings Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am Dhruv Chaudhary, and it is my honor to serve as the chairperson of the United Nations Security Council at the Shishukunj North Campus MUN Conference 2023.I am delighted to welcome you all to this committee on behalf of the entire executive bureau.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am a tenth-grader who just wants to leave a mark on this world. I am a bit of a workaholic and am mostly engaged in some activity or another. When I am not buried under a heap of work, I can be seen vibing to Polyphia or Call Me Karizma with my guitar. I am also a voracious reader who enjoys mystery novels. Along with this, I am also a football enthusiast and an ardent supporter of the Mercedes AMG-Petronas Formula One Team.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I attended my first MUN in the year 2021. As a first-time delegate, I too was a bundle of nerves and had absolutely no will to speak up in front of my seniors. However, it was the supportive bureau that brought me out of my comfort zone and helped me blossom into a passionate public speaker, thus bringing me to this platform, where I stand as your chairperson.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">MUNs have played a major role in my personality development. I have instilled a sense of diplomacy, confidence, cooperation, and discipline in my life. I truly hope to do justice to my position as chairperson of this committee and ensure that all of you have an enriching MUN experience.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I can assure you that this session of the Security Council will be full of surprises and will keep you on your toes. The committee is a crisis committee, so it will require all delegates to work even harder than a regular GA or ECOSOC committee. Immense research, knowledge of the agenda, and quick and analytical thinking will pave the way to your success.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">If there is one thing I can guarantee you, it is that no doubts or questions of yours will go unanswered, however silly they may seem. Feel free to reach out to me in case of any queries regarding the ROP or the agenda, or if you simply hate Red Bull too.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Prepare well and buckle up for an exhilarating MUN filled with fiery debates and discussions. I look forward to meeting all of you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Warm Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Dhruv Chaudhary</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Chairperson</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">United Nations Security Council</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Security Council (UNSC) plays a crucial role in international affairs by promoting global peace and security. Composed of 15 member states, including five permanent members with veto power, it deliberates on pressing issues, authorizes military interventions, and imposes sanctions. The UNSC serves as a platform for diplomatic negotiations and conflict resolution, striving to prevent conflicts and maintain stability. Its decisions carry significant weight and influence in shaping the course of international relations and addressing threats to international peace.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Addressing The South China Sea Conflict</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The South China Sea has been a long-disputed area with various countries such as Vietnam, Thailand, Malaysia, Taiwan, Brunei and China establishing their EEZ over this area. It is an area of economic importance that lies in large reserves of oil, natural gas, and aquatic life among others and has trade routes amounting up to $5.3 trillion annually. Various nations hold conflicting claims over this region and follow various policies and commit various crimes to uphold their claims. The rising tensions can act as a tipping point for World War III.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1065,"linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/shishukunj_unsc_study-guide-1.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unsc-2.webp?w=141" alt="" class="wp-image-1065" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"95px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tRu41CeZZ1xXfL0Q_o85ZG2miPL6t08r/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:95px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior UNHRC]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-unhrc/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 10:12:24 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=662</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unhrc-bg.png","id":1254,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1254 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unhrc-bg.png)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS Human Rights Commission</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.5rem">Agenda: Assessing the Human Rights Violations in Armed Conflicts with emphasis on Somalia</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3953,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9718-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3953" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br><br>Namaste, with immense pleasure I would like to welcome you all to the Shishukunj Model United Nations Conference 2023. I am Lakshya Bidasaria and I am privileged to serve as the Chairperson of The United Nations Human Rights Council. As an ambitious student, I want to achieve as many things in school as possible and I assure you that MUN is a great way to do it. I am currently in Grade 11 and being a commerce with core math student, I aspire to start my own business venture in the future. In just a year or so, MUNs have transformed my life and I went from being an inexperienced first timer to serving as your Chairperson. I will try my level best to ensure that each delegate achieves their full potential and becomes more confident as an individual.<br><br>UNHRC is the most human part of the UN with the vital requirement of sensitivity, empathy, reflection, and compassion that protects humans from humans and gives us the ladder tall enough to reach the pinnacle of civilization. This year we aim to discuss the disastrous effects armed conflicts have on human rights with a special emphasis on the violation of human rights in the country of Somalia who has been bogged up in a civil war since 1991. The livelihoods of the people living in such areas are completely uprooted due to internal as well as external conflicts and it is up to us to ensure that there is a safeguard of the basic rights of humans guaranteed by the UN charter.<br><br>Looking forward to meeting you this August.<br><br>Yours sincerely<br><strong>Lakshya Bidasaria<br>Chairperson<br>United Nations Human Rights Commission</strong><br>lakshya.bidasaria.sjc3194@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Human Rights Council was established in 2006 by Resolution 60/251 as a subsidiary body to the UN General Assembly. It replaced the former Commission on Human Rights, which operated from 1946 to 2006. The mandate of UNHRC was established in the 60/251 General Assembly Resolution, and is effective since 15 March 2006. The Human Rights Commission serves as an essential and integral part of the United Nations, for citizens are the world and the world is the citizens.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda :  Assessing the Human Rights Violations in Armed Conflicts with emphasis on Somalia</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Somalia has been without a functioning central government since the late dictator General Mohamed Siad Barre was ousted in 1991.Competition for resources and power, repression by the military regime and the colonial legacy are the background causes of the conict are thought to be the main reasons for the conflict. Furthermore foreign intervention has made things worse. The committee is expected to act and identify and support structures which will tend to strengthen and solidify peace in order to avoid a relapse into conict.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2617,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://href.li/?https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ii8v3XkSwaOi5BZ28yN2cB3lqtUu7k-F/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/unhrc-.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2617" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNHRC</strong></figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior Ad Hoc]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-adhoc/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 10:16:19 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=665</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/indian_soldiers_on_patrol_during_the_1962_sino-indian_border_war-one_one.jpeg","id":5067,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-5067 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/indian_soldiers_on_patrol_during_the_1962_sino-indian_border_war-one_one.jpeg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"},"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-size:3rem">Ad Hoc</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.5rem"},"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-size:1.5rem">Agenda: Reassessing Indo - China Relations with Emphasis on the Situation in Arunachal Pradesh</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3963,"width":232,"height":341,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/rajat-agrawal-1-edited.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3963" style="width:232px;height:341px" width="232" height="341" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Delegates,<br>With immense pleasure, I, Rajat Agrawal, welcome you all to the Shishukunj Model United Nations, 2023. It is my honor to serve as the chairperson of the Ad Hoc committee.&nbsp;<br><br>I am an eleventh-grader who is pursuing Physics, Chemistry, and Maths as my major subjects. I am also keenly interested in reading about international relations and diplomacy. Skills like public speaking, participating in debates, and negotiating serve as a stimulant to my mind. I have been MUNing for the last 4 years and have an inclination towards crisis committees. I even love to play cricket, listen to music, or write something whenever I get time from my monotonous to-do list.&nbsp;<br><br>Ad - Hoc is a temporary committee created specifically with the purpose of solving emergency debates. It is dissolved once the issue is tackled. The agenda of the committee is revealed to the delegates anywhere from 48 hours before the conference to the first committee session.&nbsp;<br><br>This years Ad-Hoc will be a continuous crisis committee, therefore the delegates should not only be well-researched with subtopics mentioned in the guide but also with the basic geopolitical framework of the world. The delegates should be aware of the current international conflicts and carry a basic idea of international relations between the countries for a fruitful MUN experience. Cant wait to meet you all and hear your perspectives!<br><br>All the Best!<br><br>Regards,<strong><br>Rajat Agrawal&nbsp;<br>Chairperson </strong><br><strong>Ad  Hoc</strong><br>rajat.agrawal.sjc2055@shishukunj.in</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Created specifically with the purpose of solving emergency debates, Adhoc is a temporary United Nations committee. It is dissolved once the issue is tackled. The agenda of the committee is revealed to the delegates anywhere from 48 hours before the conference to the first committee session.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Reassessing Indo - China Relations with Emphasis on the Situation in Arunachal Pradesh</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The agenda is formulated to tackle the military, economic and geographical conflicts between the Republic of India and The People's Republic of China. The freeze sate is 30th April 2023. The agenda provides a forum to reshape the diplomatic ties between two of the most powerful nations in the World. The committee will be primarily dealing with that "Agreement Between the Governments of Republic of India and People's Republic of China on Confidence Building Measures in the Military Field Along the Line of Actual Control in the India-China Border Areas,1996" and would aim to solve the major loopholes of this agreement.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNICEF]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-unicef/</link>

  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unicef.jpg","id":916,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-916" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unicef.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>

<!-- wp:spacer -->
<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
