<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">United Nations International Children's <br>Emergency Fund 1</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>D</strong>eveloping <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>S</strong>olutions to <strong>P</strong>rotect the <strong>R</strong>ight to <strong>E</strong>ducation of <strong>C</strong>hildren</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3625,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0108.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3625" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Dear delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am Parisha Munoth, and it is an immense pleasure and an honor to serve as the chairperson of UNICEF. I heartily welcome you all to the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus MUN.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am currently studying in grade 11 and wish to pursue law through the National Law University of Bangalore. I also like economics, which motivated me to study commerce with legal studies. I consider myself a skilled orator and a talkative person by nature. Apart from talking, I love painting and reading. I would prefer anything but classics in books and Van Gough in painting.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am a very approachable and friendly person, open to every conversation, especially the ones about Brooklyn Nine-Nine. I am more than thrilled to be a part of this bureau, and I expect all the delegates to be truly engaged with the committee. I wish to make this MUN the most memorable one by ensuring exciting and informative sessions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">As the chairperson of the committee, the delegates are free to approach me with any questions, confusion, or concerns via email. I will make sure every delegate gets a platform to express themselves without hesitation and that their opinions and suggestions get the right recognition. I am waiting for this wonderful journey to begin and look forward to meeting all of you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">All the best for the committee sessions, and happy researching!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700">Parisha Munoth<br>Chairperson<br>UNICEF</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Commitee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">UNICEF, the United Nations International Children's Emergency Fund, is a global organization dedicated to advocating for children's rights and ensuring their well-being. Operating in over 190 countries, UNICEF provides humanitarian aid, healthcare, education, and protection to children in need. It works closely with governments, NGOs, and communities to address issues such as child mortality, malnutrition, lack of access to clean water, and inadequate education. Through its programs and initiatives, UNICEF strives to create a world where every child has the opportunity to thrive, grow, and reach their full potential.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>D</strong>eveloping <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>S</strong>olutions to <strong>P</strong>rotect the <strong>R</strong>ight to <strong>E</strong>ducation of <strong>C</strong>hildren</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Education is one of the most important criteria for economic development in ones country. It has come to our attention that education is not being provided at its best in every part of the world which is a major issue as barriers like gender, poverty, and hunger come in between. Education not being provided leads to an increased crime rate. Developing sustainable solutions to protect the right to education will provide children with access to it and thus will help in future developments. UNICEF is taking action regarding the same and hopes that every child in this world gets access to education.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/shishukunj_unicef_mun-conference-2023.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unicef-removebg-preview.png?w=457" alt="" class="wp-image-4592" style="width:130px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNDP 1]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-undp1/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 15:49:15 +0000</pubDate>

  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=722</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/undp-2.jpg","id":1973,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1973" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/undp-2.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","overlayBackgroundColor":"background","overlayTextColor":"background","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMME 1</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>educing <strong>A</strong>ir <strong>P</strong>ollution in <strong>C</strong>ities <strong>U</strong>sing <strong>S</strong>ustainable and <strong>M</strong>odern&nbsp;<strong>T</strong>echnology</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"152px"} -->
<div style="height:152px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3602,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0122.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3602" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Dear delegates,<br>I am Innaya Khan, and I will be serving as the chairperson of the United Nations Development Programme. It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you to the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus MUN.<br><br>I am a 10th grader who hasnt yet decided on what her future will be but is sure about one thing: she doesnt have dreams; she has goals. MUN conferences have not only enhanced my public speaking skills and developed a unique sense of open-mindedness, but they have also given me an opportunity to create a strong mindset.<br><br>I am honored and excited to have been given this opportunity for such a great experience. I hope the delegates put in all their efforts and try to grasp the concept of the agenda as well as the subtopics. As the chairperson of this committee, I would love to see the delegates have fun and also take a lot of good memories with them. I also expect to see some creative ideas to combat air pollution.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Lastly, I want my delegates to know that I am quite an amiable person and that I understand that this MUN conference is the first of many to come for most delegates. So if you have any doubt, feel free to approach me anytime.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700">Cheerio! <br>Innaya Khan<br>Chairperson<br>United Nations Development Programme</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) is a global organization that focuses on promoting sustainable development and eradicating poverty worldwide. Operating in over 170 countries, UNDP works closely with governments, civil society, and the private sector to tackle pressing challenges, such as inequality, climate change, and gender empowerment. It provides technical expertise, resources, and policy advice to support countries in achieving their development goals. UNDP plays a crucial role in fostering inclusive growth, resilience, and sustainable development, aiming to improve the lives of people around the world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : Reducing Air Pollution in Cities Using Sustainable and Modern&nbsp;Technology</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Air pollution is one of the most well-known issues that every nation on Earth has to deal with. It has an impact on the environment, our health, and our way of life as a whole. While there are many potential causes for this pollution, human activity accounts for the majority of them. Since humans have advanced so much, it is only reasonable to assume that they will create technologies to clean up the earth and reduce air pollution. In conclusion, UNDP will try its best to form a resolution that balances the needs of humans and does not compromise the safety of the environment.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNHCR]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-unhcr/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 15:52:50 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=727</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unhcr-2599856766-e1684693400590.jpg","id":1820,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1820" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unhcr-2599856766-e1684693400590.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","overlayBackgroundColor":"background","overlayTextColor":"background","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer -->
<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase","fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS HIGH COMMISSIONER FOR REFUGEES</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>M</strong>ethods to <strong>T</strong>ackle the <strong>M</strong>iddle <strong>E</strong>astern <strong>R</strong>efugee <strong>C</strong>risis</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3610,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0123.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3610" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Namaste!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">With immense pride, I, Shourya Singh Chauhan, am thrilled to welcome you to the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus MUN Conference 2023. As a 10th grader with a heart full of ambition and a mind full of MUNs, I will be serving as the Chairperson of UNHCR.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">A lifelong learner with curiosity as insatiable as my appetite for paneer butter masala, I am also a master of offbeat tonguesJapanese, Sanskrit, Telugu, French, and even a bit of Viking language (just kidding, or am I?). I have big dreams and aspire to become an IFS officer, polyglot dog rescuer, and medical engineer. But don't let that fool youI'm like anyone else with a confessed addiction to all things anime and K-pop. Need a break from discussing diplomatic policies or geeking out about BTS or Naruto? Then I'm your guy. Trust me, once we start nailing those resolutions and making some serious progress, the fun will come naturally.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Delegates, we only have two days to discuss the agenda and draft resolution, so I hope we all work together efficiently and methodically. I know you all are fantastic debaters with brilliant ideas, however there may be times when we can't come to a consensus, but we can always resort to a game of rock-paper-scissors. (I'm serious this time!)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Let us not forget the ultimate goal here: to leave this committee with cherished memories and knowledge aplenty. So, with all that said, I leave the mammoth task of determining the committee flow in your capable hands. Feel free to reach out with any concerns whatsoever. Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color"><strong>Shourya Singh Chouhan<br>Chairperson<br>UNHCR</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR) is a specialized agency mandated to protect and support refugees, forcibly displaced individuals, and stateless people worldwide. With a primary goal of ensuring the fundamental rights and well-being of refugees, UNHCR provides emergency assistance, shelter, healthcare, education, and legal protection. It works in close collaboration with governments, NGOs, and other partners to find durable solutions for refugees, including voluntary repatriation, local integration, or resettlement in a third country. Through its efforts, UNHCR plays a vital role in alleviating human suffering and advocating for the rights of those displaced by conflict and persecution.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : Methods to Tackle the Middle Eastern Refugee Crisis</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">To achieve long-term peace, the Middle East refugee problem is a crucial issue that needs to be handled right away. The main objectives of this agenda are securing refugee resettlement, safeguarding refugees' fundamental rights, resolving the acute identity crisis, and ensuring dignity, as well as providing funding and other guidelines for creating civil infrastructure. It is the responsibility of UNHCR to end this international disaster.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":3223,"width":"118px","height":"100px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/09/shishukunj_unhcr_mun-conference-2023.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/whatsapp-image-2023-06-24-at-22.39.02.jpg?w=285" alt="" class="wp-image-3223" style="object-fit:cover;width:118px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DFK2jnvO4Nr9C7u3ntcgPMsc64dNkAMhAAwQqEA3dOk/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus Lok Sabha]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-lok-sabha/</link>
  <pubDate>Tue, 09 May 2023 15:56:12 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=733</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lok_sabha-e1687364327237.jpeg","id":2823,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2823" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/lok_sabha-e1687364327237.jpeg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"53px"} -->
<div style="height:53px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">LOK SABHA</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>eviewing the <strong>C</strong>urrent <strong>S</strong>tatus of <strong>D</strong>emocracy in <strong>I</strong>ndia</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"152px"} -->
<div style="height:152px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":3581,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a0094.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3581" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"textTransform":"capitalize"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8;text-transform:capitalize"><strong>Letter from the chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Namaste Parliamentarians,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">With esteemed honor, I, Parth Lahoti, welcome you to the Shishukunj North Campus MUN 2023 and am fortunate enough to serve as the Speaker for the only Indian committee of this conference, the Lok Sabha.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I am a 10th grader, and I aspire to study science in my higher classes. This will be my fourth year of Model United Nations. I engage myself in music and art while also being a national-title-winning wildlife photographer. Being a stock market investor and finance enthusiast, I also like to deliberate on Indian politics.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Lok Sabha is a very debating and dynamic committee that is responsible for the legislative, budget, and executive functions of the country. Being a senior and important committee, we plan to have extensive discussions on the smallest of issues that the country is facing. The agenda for this year is set as Deliberation on the Current Status of Democracy in India, keeping in mind the diversification and practicality of the agenda and subtopics.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I would entertain all the points and discussions, but I would like the committee to be patriotically serious. If you have any doubts of any sort, do not hesitate to drop me an email. I look forward to meeting the emerging politicians of the nation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Jai Hind!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Sincerely,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Parth Lahoti</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Speaker</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Lok Sabha</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The Lok Sabha is the lower house of the Parliament of India and is the representative body of the people. Comprising elected members from various constituencies across the country, it plays a significant role in the legislative process. The Lok Sabha's primary functions include enacting laws, scrutinizing the government's activities, and representing the interests of the citizens. It serves as a platform for discussions, debates, and decision-making on crucial national issues. The Lok Sabha is a cornerstone of India's democratic system, ensuring people's participation and accountability in governance.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : Reviewing the Current Status of Democracy in India</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">India is considered the mother of democracy. The preamble states to form a "Sovereign Socialist Secular Democratic Republic." The nation has always been a big exponent of the universal adult franchise since its independence and believes in the fundamentals of equality, humanity, representation, and freedom, i.e., democracy. Numerous concerns have arisen, encompassing limitations on individual freedoms and the infringement of fundamental rights. Recent actions by the government have curtailed freedom of expression and speech, with apparent disregard for the humanitarian rights of minority communities. Furthermore, the impartiality of the judiciary has come under scrutiny due to allegations of government interference. In light of recent events, we have chosen our agenda as "Reviewing the Current Status of Democracy in India". Here, we would deliberate on this agenda, as the country shares its feelings and emotions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":1055,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/lok_sabha_study_guide.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/lok-sabha-2.webp?w=400" alt="" class="wp-image-1055" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7333333333333333","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"thumbnail","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-thumbnail is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/lok_sabha-rule_of_procedure-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp?w=97" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="aspect-ratio:0.7333333333333333;object-fit:cover;width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">ROP</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7333333333333333","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"thumbnail","linkDestination":"none","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-thumbnail is-resized loud"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp?w=97" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="aspect-ratio:0.7333333333333333;object-fit:cover;width:78px;height:auto" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">General Assembly</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase">Shishukunj MUN | North Campus</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":4979,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/60a0073.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-4979" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>LETTER FROM THE USG-GA</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">Dear Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I, Tanisha Bhojwani, am honored to serve as the Under Secretary General for General Assembly (USG-GA) for the first ever Shishukunj North Campus Model United Nations. I have been part of MUN's for the past 5 years. I am a 12th grader pursuing PCM with Commercial Arts. Apart from my inclination towards science, I am an ardent artist and a devoted dancer. The direct way to my heart is through a cup of frappe and a serving of momos or pizza. I believe I am an approachable person, always open to conversations, be it fun or intellectual. The best thing I<br>like about MUNs apart from generous socialization is that it stimulates a sense of seriousness and curiosity in a delegate which pushes him/her to ponder and confer about myriad cases like the actual drug cartels being dealt with, citizens being denied rights, children starving in refugee camps and epidemics of deadly diseases spreading across nations rather than plagiarizing solutions and statements from a random news report.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">For MUN 2023, I would like all the participants to put in charge their researching, thinking and speaking ability. MUN's are a lot more than just debating. It's a platform to explore, grow and enhance your public and leadership skills. At this conference, you will have the opportunity to engage in stimulating committee sessions, assume the roles of diplomats, and represent the interests of assigned countries. The theme for this year, 'Achieving Peace Dignity And Harmony Through Integrated Development' is a revolutionary header in itself. It forces us to reflect upon the past and make amends for a better global future. The Conferences aim to foster critical thinking, leadership abilities, and a deep understanding of international relations, all of which are essential skills for your personal and academic growth. I look forward to enthusiastic participation, witty discussions and unparalleled solutions from all the committees. </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The wide and diverse committees under the general assembly have something for everyone. From setting a platform for discussion, negotiation, and advocacy for problems involving disarmament, global challenges, and threats to international peace in DISEC to LOK SABHA aiming to bring to light whether democracy is being served or it is really that 'the law is blind'; we deal with many highlighted and hidden problems. Amidst the seriousness and urgency to resolve the issues, it is important to note that the General Assembly's work is guided by the principles of sovereign equality, multilateralism, and the pursuit of the common good for all member states. The GA provides a platform for dialogue, cooperation, and collective decision- making to address the challenges and opportunities facing the international community. The bureau this year has worked very hard to make it a comfortable experience for anyone irrespective of your prior experience. I hope that this MUN is a success. I am overwhelmed to welcome you all and I eagerly look forward to meeting you all. </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">So, delegates, fasten your seat belts for this memorable, fun and enlightening ride where all your thoughts will be heard, and skills tested.<br>For any queries or doubts feel free to approach your bureau or me via email.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color"><strong>Welcoming you all<br>Yours truly</strong>,<br><img class="wp-image-3202" style="width: 150px" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/usg-ga-e1687707307670.jpg" alt=""><strong><br>Tanisha Bhojwani <br>Under Secretary General- General Assembly</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->

<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1027,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus ECOSOC]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-ecosoc/</link>
  <pubDate>Wed, 10 May 2023 18:01:40 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=967</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/ecosoc.jpg","id":1085,"dimRatio":80,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|40","left":"var:preset|spacing|40"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-80 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1085" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/ecosoc.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">ECONOMIC AND SOCIAL COUNCIL</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase">Shishukunj MUN | North Campus</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":4994,"width":"204px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/60a0075.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-4994" style="width:204px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>LETTER FROM THE USG</strong>: <strong>ECOSOC</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I, Nikunj Rathi, will serve as the Under-Secretary-General: ECOSOC for the first iteration of the Shishukunj North Campus Model United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">As an aspiring medical student with a keen interest in the sciences, my longing for logic has led me to examine various disciplines, including geopolitics  the battleground of the world and an intense game of ideologies, power, control, and economics. It suffices to say that if you have waddled through the labyrinth of this very dynamic game, you have familiarized yourself with the ways of the world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">We ensure that this MUN will be a lifetime experience for first-timers and the experienced, and we vouch for a great level of debate. The Economic and Social Council (ECOSOC), central to the United Nations System, advances three dimensions of sustainable development: economic, social, and environmental. I aim for it to be an incubator that fosters research skills, debate, teamwork, and innovative thinking during the course of this conference.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The committees this year tackle major global issues. Topics as intricate and complex as the need for a new global reserve currency to simple yet paramount topics, including the need to reduce the negative impact of plastic on the environment, would be deliberated upon by the World Bank and the United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP). Social issues such as education and universal health coverage will also be contemplated in detail by the United Nations Commission on Social Development (UNCSD) and the World Health Organization (WHO).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">I hope the agendas intrigue you and the MUN helps you explore a fresh viewpoint of the world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Happy researching!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Yours sincerely,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":3060,"width":"191px","height":"62px","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/signature-final-1-e1687505987295.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3060" style="width:191px;height:62px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Nikunj Rathi</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Under-Secretary-General</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","lineHeight":"0"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">ECOSOC</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committees</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1431,"width":"120px","height":"100px","scale":"cover","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->

  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior FAO 1]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-fao-i/</link>
  <pubDate>Wed, 10 May 2023 18:35:26 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=985</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/urban-farming-2048x1364-transformed-1.jpeg","id":1229,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1229" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/urban-farming-2048x1364-transformed-1.jpeg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-background-color"><strong>F</strong>OOD AND <strong>A</strong>GRICULTURE <strong>O</strong>RGANIZATION 1</mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.2rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.2rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><strong>Agenda</strong>: Ensuring Global Food Security and Agriculture Growth</mark></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4712,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/yashvi-edited-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4712" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br>I'm delighted to welcome you all to the first ever Junior Shishukunj Model United Nations conference. I, Yashvi Rawat, am honored to serve as the chairperson of the Food and Agricultural Organization 1.<br><br>I'm an 11th grader studying commerce with applied mathematics. Aside from my great passion for dance and being a fashion aficionado, you can also catch me having debates on several controversial topics. Ive participated in multiple MUNs now and Ive grown to love the experience, but I still remember my first MUN as a sixth grader. I remember being clueless, and absolutely chaotic, but I can assure you I'll try my very best to make Shishukunj MUN 2023 an experience altogether enjoyable and enriching for all.&nbsp;<br><br>In today's world innovation and collaboration can help you reach the solution to any problem. Remembering that, I expect the delegates to discuss our committee's agenda which deals with the necessity of achieving global food security, agricultural advancement and creation of a greener environment for all.&nbsp;<br><br>I genuinely cannot wait to meet you all and hear all of your opinions as well as creative solutions to many of the current pressing issues. Feel free to reach out in case you're ever in need of guidance and I'll be happy to help!<br><br>Regards<br><strong>Yashvi Rawat</strong><br><strong>Chairperson</strong><br><strong>FAO 1</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The United Nations' Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO) is a specialized body that oversees global initiatives to end hunger, increase agricultural productivity, raise the standard of living in rural populations and contribute towards global economic growth. FAO operates in more than 130 nations around the world and has 195 members, including 194 countries and the European Union. It aids in the coordination of government and the development agency works towards the advancement and development of agribusiness, forestry, fisheries, and land and water resources. Additionally, it carries out research, offers technical assistance, runs educational and training initiatives, and compiles statistics on agricultural output, production, and advancement.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Ensuring Global Food Security and Agriculture Growth</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">By 2050, it is anticipated that there will be over 9 billion people on the planet, which will result in a significant rise in the need for food. For the purpose of feeding the world's expanding population and eradicating poverty and hunger, it is essential to ensure global food security and agricultural expansion.&nbsp; Food security is the state in which all individuals consistently have physical, social, and economic access to an adequate supply of food that is safe and nutritious and satisfies their dietary requirements for an active and healthy lifestyle. Climate change, population growth, rising food costs, and environmental stresses will all have major but unknowable effects on food security during the ensuing decades. The world urgently needs adaptation techniques and policy solutions that address choices for managing water allocation, land use patterns, commerce in food, postharvest food processing, and food costs and safety. The Food and Agriculture Organization aims to discuss and arrive at solutions that can be implemented worldwide to solve the issue at hand.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":2506,"width":246,"height":249,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QMEMGPIMiuQ32xMFwfKS9DvChk0ic3uD/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/fao_logo.svg_-1.png?w=640" alt="" class="wp-image-2506" style="width:246px;height:249px" width="246" height="249" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Study Guide</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3032,"width":211,"height":243,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/fao1.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pdf_file_icon.svg_.png?w=640" alt="" class="wp-image-3032" style="width:211px;height:243px" width="211" height="243" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Allotments</strong></figcaption></figure>
