  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Senior About Us]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/aksh-jhalaria-senior-about-us/</link>
  <pubDate>Fri, 12 May 2023 09:47:35 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>akshgarg13</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun4.wordpress.com/?page_id=1243</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/dji_0104.jpg","id":3795,"hasParallax":true,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3795 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/dji_0104.jpg)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem">ABOUT US</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong>History</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Shishukunj Model United Nations emerged in 2015, evolved as a platform for diplomatic deliberation about global issues, and is going to elevate itself in its eighth iteration as a one-of-a-kind conference where students will strive to learn from their peers while finding solutions to issues at handboth from the past and present.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong>The UN4MUN Procedure</strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Although most Model UN conferences have adopted the UNA-USA rules of procedure, the UN4MUN procedure remains one of Shishukunj MUNs most proud and significant features. As prescribed by the United Nations Department of Public Information, this procedure ensures that each delegate is of equal importance in the committee, making it a realistic simulation of the United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong><strong>Functional Excellence</strong></strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With an inextinguishable passion for perfection, the Secretariat, Bureau, and Organising Committee of the Shishukunj MUN are sure to make this conference fruitful for every delegate, no matter their experience.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong><strong>A Forum for Fundamental Deliberation</strong></strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This year, the senior edition of the Shishukunj MUN brings forward twelve innovative and dynamic committees with agendas spanning across disciplines, making sure that all voices are heard. With the promise of being a forum for healthy debate, this conference is always open to unconventional ideas and questions that aim to change the world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><div role="img" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1292 has-parallax" style="background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unccpcj-bg-1.png)"></div><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->

<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":60} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1000px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1000px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":329,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"179px"} -->
<div style="height:179px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.3rem">UNITED NATIONS COMMISSION ON CRIME PREVENTION AND CRIMINAL JUSTICE</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1rem">Agenda:  Unveiling the Links between Terrorism and Organized Crimes - Mapping the Interconnections to Counter Terrorism&nbsp;at&nbsp;its&nbsp;Source</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"311px"} -->
<div style="height:311px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter from the Co Chairpersons</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4041,"width":444,"height":336,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/60a9695.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-4041" style="object-fit:cover" width="444" height="336" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true}} -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br><br>We, Ansh Agarwal and Parth Khandelwal, take immense pleasure in welcoming you to the Shishukunj Model United Nations 2023!&nbsp; We feel honored to serve as the co-chairpersons of UNCCPCJ. As Co-chairpersons we will also be serving as your guides &amp; cheerleaders.<br><br>I, Ansh Agarwal, am an experienced MUNer and have also won an award in the prestigious Harvard MUN in the past. I have also served as a bureau member in the last edition of the Shishukunj MUN.I am a PCMB student and am known for my Danny Ricardo-like infectious energy. I am big on Bollywood and people describe life feeling like a Bollywood movie around me. I also love F1 and look up to drivers like Lewis Hamilton , Sebastian Vettel(ex driver) &amp; Charles Le Clerec!!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>I am Parth Khandelwal, a 12th grade commerce with Applied Mathematics student who has done 5 MUNs. I am known to be a multitasker .I am a football fan and love the team Chelsea. I play squash and used to play guitar. I also love binge watching movies and series especially crime and action, I also love the music of King &amp; The Weekend!!<br><br>We plan to have an engaging and lively discussion on the agenda "Tracing the Ripple Effects of Terrorist Attacks and Their Links to Other Criminal Activities"<br>The agenda is unique in the truest of sense as the agenda will discuss terrorism at source, the world has talked about terrorism time and again but hasn't ever been completely successful to stop it! The committee aims to stop terrorism from its roots . Everything that makes terrorism happen is what the committee will deal with, from terror financing to the links of terrorism with organized crime such as counterfeiting, drug &amp; weapon smuggling, illegal mining etc.<br><br>At the end lets make these 3 days unforgettable to last us all a lifetime &amp; let this be a journey of discovery, collaboration &amp; learning.<br>Accio productive debate!!!<br><br>Best Regards,<br><strong>Ansh Agarwal and Parth Khandelwal<br>Co-Chairpersons<br>United Nations Commission on Crime Prevention and Criminal Justice</strong><br>ansh.agarwal.sjc2138@shishukunj.in and parth.khandelwal.sjc2296@shishukunj.in<br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">UNCCPCJ knows "Band-aids don't fix bullet holes" and is the principal policy making body of the UN in the field of crime prevention and criminal justice. The CCPCJ also provides Member States with a forum for exchanging knowledge, experience, and data in order to create national and international policies and and to identify priorities for combating crime. The functions of CCPCJ include offering policy guidance in the area of crime prevention and criminal justice ; designing , monitoring and reviewing the implementation of the UN crime Program and the Planning and the management of UN&nbsp;Crime&nbsp;Congress</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda :  Unveiling the Links between Terrorism and Organized Crimes - Mapping the Interconnections to Counter Terrorism&nbsp;at&nbsp;its&nbsp;Source</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>UNCCPCJ will discuss terrorism at source.The committee will look into the linkages between organised crime and terrorism.the committee will also discuss the funding of terrorism and cyber terrorism while looking into fronts for terrorism which are nightmares dressed like&nbsp;daydreams.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"color":{"text":"#076be3"}}} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#076be3;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Study Guide</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":2634,"width":150,"height":150,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1geiQ-Uuko8v9sjRYuGhT7G_O474smPt4/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/unccpcj.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-2634" style="width:150px;height:150px" width="150" height="150" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>UNCCPCJ</strong></figcaption></figure>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2932" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/dji_0001.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1,"style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0"}},"typography":{"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase","fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-background-color has-text-color" style="padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;font-size:2.4rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><strong>SHISHUKUNJ MUN 2023</strong></h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"small"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color">Jhalaria</mark></strong></mark></strong> <strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color">JUNIOR </mark></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0"},"margin":{"top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0"}}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size" style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbd" class="has-inline-color"><strong>R</strong>evolutionary<strong> I</strong>nterchange of Ideas for <strong>S</strong>ustainable<strong>E</strong>cosystems</mark></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"154px"} -->
<div style="height:154px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":4772,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/bi22404-4.jpg?w=881" alt="" class="wp-image-4772" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"right","textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-right has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">LETTER FROM THE <strong>SECRETARY GENERAL</strong></mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br>On behalf of the entire organizing committee, it gives me immense pleasure to welcome you to the first edition of the Shishukunj Model United Nations Jhalaria Junior, which is to be held from August 4, 2023, to August 5, 2023.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p> Perhaps now more than ever, our international community has faced change after change. It has seen political systems, pandemics, and international crises follow one another, each consuming the previous one. Despite this, we constantly live on this ever-bequeathed and ever-disappointed hope that everything will be fine, but it won't. It is not important to have an end goal in sight, we just need to play and have fun - and innovation will come out of that naturally. Keeping this in mind, I present to you the conference theme - <strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">R</mark></strong>evolutionary <strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">I</mark></strong>nterchange of<strong> </strong>Ideas for <strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">S</mark></strong>ustainable <strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">E</mark></strong>cosystems. The theme recognizes the bold actions that our generation will have to take in the coming years; people across the world need to push boundaries in order to accomplish the goals that we have set for ourselves, instead of waiting for others to take the first step, it is you who needs to be the changemaker for the world's good, to prudently and positively act upon the responsibilities that come with the role of an international leader, to imagine a better world, and work with others to achieve it.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The Shishukunj MUN - Junior will be having ten dynamic committees each with a fascinating agenda pertinent not only to the present but also to historical conflicts and futuristic regulations. Beyond the skills of debate and negotiation that the delegates will practice over the course of the conference, it is vital to realize that vision and ambition are equally as important.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Delegates and faculty advisors, it is an honor to serve as your Secretary-General. Our team cannot wait to hear your ideas and witness your intellectual curiosity. The entire Secretariat and Bureau are determined in ensuring a worthwhile experience for every student and making this MUN one of their most memorable experiences. Hoping to see you at the conference!<br><br>Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4309,"width":264,"height":119,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/whatsapp_image_2023-07-14_at_11.36.21-removebg-preview.png?w=743" alt="" class="wp-image-4309" style="width:264px;height:119px" width="264" height="119" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Stuti Desai<br>Secretary General</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":4792,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/bi22397-6.jpg?w=980" alt="" class="wp-image-4792" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><br></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"right"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-right"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#165fbe" class="has-inline-color">LETTER FROM THE <strong>DIRECTOR GENERAL</strong></mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear Delegates, </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>It gives me immense pleasure and pride to welcome you to the first iteration of the Shishukunj Model United Nations Jhalaria Junior. Organising a first-of-its-kind Junior MUN, the Secretariat and the Bureau are all set and excited to welcome you and ensure an enriching experience for all students.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>I was introduced to the world of MUNs in grade 7, where I was a scared delegate representing Lebanon in the Shishukunj MUN, with no clue about how things worked or that Delegates Decorum! is supposed to be the new keep quiet students, and now here I am, serving as the Director General of this conference. The committee room to me is like the battleground for delegates, where debates and discussions light up the rooms, them, wearing suits as armour, fighting hard to protect the interests of their respective countries.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With progress in every sphere, problems and issues have risen too, and with few rays of hope left, it is now up to us to ensure that future generations are able to see the Earth as a marvel of nature and not a wasteland. As the theme RISE : Revolutionary Interchange of Ideas for Sustainable Ecosystems suggests, it is crucial to address challenges the world faces, to find innovative solutions and ideas to make todays impossibilities, tomorrows miracles, and to build a more sustainable and secure future for all.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Lastly, I understand that MUN can seem overwhelming at first, but rest assured that our team is here to support you at every step of the conference so that you can have an unforgettable experience and make this MUN your most memorable one. So, don your armour and prepare to engage in lively debate and discourse. Hoping to see you all at the conference!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Best Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4212,"width":219,"height":118,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/whatsapp_image_2023-07-12_at_13.16.01-removebg-preview-3.png?w=279" alt="" class="wp-image-4212" style="width:219px;height:118px" width="219" height="118" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Aarna Jain<br>Director-General</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">ABOUT</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size" style="text-transform:uppercase">North Campus</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>HISTORY</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">The year 2005 marked the beginning of the Shishukunj International School, a journey to let every bud bloom and mould students to become confident leaders of tomorrow.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">A stepping stone to achieving this goal was initiating the Shishukunj Model United Nations in 2015. This three-day conference encourages delegates to vehemently pose solutions to global issues, stand for what they believe in, and broaden their worldview by inculcating varied perspectives through a comprehensive understanding of the United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color">8 years hence, yet again going a step further, we are introducing the Shishukunj North Campus MUNa medium to make shishyans globally, ethically, and culturally aware citizens. With 13 dynamic committees and a plethora of intriguing debates and discussions awaiting, this MUN will be a memorable experience for all the shishyans and a legacy for the MUNs&nbsp;yet&nbsp;to&nbsp;come!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>A FORUM FOR FUNDAMENTAL DELIBERATION</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">We cannot always build the future for our youth, but we can always build our youth for the future. An integral component of building a globally aware generation is instilling the qualities of deliberation and cooperation within them. Shishukunj MUN acts as this forum for fundamental deliberation, encouraging students to acknowledge, contemplate, and act on the universal problems at hand through a process of mutual understanding and collaboration. By engaging in quality debates and discussions, students develop an inclusive understanding of the world around them and learn to stand up for what they believe in. Developing critical thinking and emphasizing the use of logic and reason, deliberation, stands out as the key for young leaders to think, empower,&nbsp;and&nbsp;implement.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"65px"} -->
<div style="height:65px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>

<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1850" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/specialized-agencies-3552270888-e1684697040377.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns {"isStackedOnMobile":false} -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">Specialized Agencies</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase">Shishukunj MUN | North Campus</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"full","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:image {"id":4980,"width":"203px","height":"300px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/08/60a9962.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-4980" style="width:203px;height:300px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>LETTER FROM THE </strong><br><strong>USG-SPECIALISED AGENCIES</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Namaste, Delegates,</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Welcome to the Shishukunj North Campus MUN 2023. In the very first iteration, we are introducing two enthralling continuous crisis committees that will put you on the edge of your seat and will keep you on your toes throughout.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">The South China Sea conflict will be the centre of discussion in the most powerful organ of the UN-UNSC,&nbsp; while NATO will focus on its influence in the Asia Pacific region.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Crisis committees focus on the core theme of MUNs i.e. DIPLOMACY, RESEARCH, CONSENSUS, and CRITICAL THINKING. Its a common notion that crisis committees tend to be difficult and tiring but believe me, these could turn out to be the most enriching experience for you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Thorough research, spontaneity, creativity and critical thinking skills are essential for success in a crisis committee. These committees push you to think out of the box by creating certain realistic scenarios called CRISES. Your main objective in these committees will be to solve all the crises successfully and make good directives. ANY PREWRITTEN MATERIAL would not at all be helpful in these committees due to their extremely dynamic nature. So, all the delegates are advised to NOT do the same.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">I sincerely hope that by the time this conference ends, you get to learn a plethora of new things and be a better version of yourself. Please feel free to reach out to me or any of the Executive Board members, if you have any doubts or questions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"0","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"},"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:0">Regards</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5372,"width":"190px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/grerg-1.png?w=796" alt="" class="wp-image-5372" style="width:190px;height:auto" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Secretary General , Under Secretary General: Specialised Agencies and Crisis Director</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Shishukunj Model United Nations, North Campus, 2023</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committees</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"wrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1065,"width":"115px","height":"100px","scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior UNESCO 2]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-unesco-2/</link>
  <pubDate>Mon, 05 Jun 2023 18:11:08 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=1944</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/equal-and-accessible-education-in-post-covid-era.png","id":2720,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2720" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/equal-and-accessible-education-in-post-covid-era.png" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-background-color"><strong>U</strong>NITED <strong>N</strong>ATIONS <strong>E</strong>DUCATIONAL,<strong>S</strong>CIENTIFIC <strong>A</strong>ND <strong>C</strong>ULTURAL <strong>O</strong>RGANIZATION 2</mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.2rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.2rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><strong>Agenda</strong>: Equal and Accessible Education in Post-Covid Era</mark></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4839,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/shubhi-1.jpg?w=965" alt="" class="wp-image-4839" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear Delegates<br>I, Shubhi Agrawal, the Chairperson of the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization, take great pleasure in extending a warm welcome to all of you to the Junior Shishukunj Model United Nations 2023.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>As a 10th grader who's continuously exploring and embracing every opportunity that comes my way, I am thrilled to be part of this prestigious event. Alongside my academic pursuits, I have cultivated various hobbies, I'm particularly fond of dancing, especially kathak, painting, badminton, and writing, among many others. I have a deep appreciation for music and shows, constantly seeking out new and exciting recommendations.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This moment fills me with immense honour and privilege as I reflect upon my journey. It feels like just yesterday when I took part in my first MUN back in 2020. Little did I know then that I would be writing this letter as the chairperson today.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The agenda of our committee UNESCO 2 is Equal and Accessible Education in Post-Covid Era. The Agenda aims to discuss and find effective solutions to these issues, emphasising the importance of adaptability in an ever-changing world. The COVID-19 pandemic has had a diverse impact on students' education, particularly in countries with limited resources, further highlighting the need for adaptable approaches to teaching and learning.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>I would very much appreciate it if the delegates can find new realms in the agenda and bring them forth to the committee. The study guide is by no means the end of the research.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Quality research combined with good argumentation and a solid representation of facts is what constitutes an excellent performance. I encourage you all to utilize as much original thinking as possible. I am confident that the Shishukunj MUN 2023 will be an enriching experience for all.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you have any queries or concerns, do not hesitate to contact me. We will be doing our best to ensure that this will be a fruitful experience for all of you. Looking forward to meeting yall at the conference.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Regards<br><strong>Shubhi Agrawal&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Chairperson</strong><br><strong>UNESCO 2&nbsp;</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>UNESCO, the United Nations Educational, Scientific, and Cultural Organization, was established on 16 November 1945. With 195 Members and 8 Associate Members, it operates under the guidance of the General Conference and the Executive Board. The implementation of decisions made by these bodies is carried out by the Secretariat, which is led by the Director-General. Headquartered in Paris, UNESCO maintains over 50 field offices across the globe.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>UNESCO&nbsp; contributes to peace and security by Promoting quality education for all, Mobilizing scientific knowledge and policies to support sustainable development, eradicating poverty,&nbsp; Addressing emerging social challenges, Nurturing cultural diversity, Building inclusive knowledge societies through information and communication. By focusing on these objectives, UNESCO aims to make significant contributions to the betterment of humanity, fostering progress and cooperation on a global scale.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Equal and Accessible Education in Post-Covid&nbsp;era</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The agenda was decided keeping in mind the need to discuss solutions to make education accessible to all, particularly for those who are at the risk of falling behind. The Agenda not only aims at discussing these issues but also at deliberating its solutions.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>COVID-19 is a global issue that needs the world's cooperation and coordination for reducing its effects. The pandemic has completely changed people's way of life in every corner of the world. The COVID-19 pandemic impacted all spheres of life and education was not an exception. In March 2020, the world health organization declared it as a global pandemic causing transformation and changes in education.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Throughout history, teaching and learning have undergone various transformations. The COVID-19 pandemic has had a diverse impact on students' education, particularly in countries with limited resources compared to those with more abundant resources.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The pandemic has shed light on the existing disparities within our education systems. With the closure of schools and universities, students have had to rely on online platforms for learning, creating difficulties for those without access to digital infrastructure. The most severely affected by the pandemic were learners belonging to marginalized groups who lacked access to digital learning opportunities.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Further, this Agenda emphasizes on the importance of adaptability in an ever changing world and to recognize the need to remain flexible to face the emerging challenges and global shifts. It is an opportunity to create a stronger and innovative education system for the future.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":1201,"width":213,"height":161,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/n-merged.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/d890a-unesco-logo.webp?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-1201" style="width:213px;height:161px" width="213" height="161" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Study Guide</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3032,"width":144,"height":166,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unesco2.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pdf_file_icon.svg_.png?w=640" alt="" class="wp-image-3032" style="width:144px;height:166px" width="144" height="166" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Allotments</strong></figcaption></figure>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior DISEC]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-disec/</link>
  <pubDate>Sat, 03 Jun 2023 13:03:09 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=2089</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/screenshot-2023-06-13-115040.png","id":2340,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","isDark":false,"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull is-light" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2340" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/screenshot-2023-06-13-115040.png" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-background-color"><strong>D</strong>ISARMAMENT AND <strong>I</strong>NTERNATIONAL <strong>S</strong>ECURITY <strong>C</strong>OUNCIL</mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.2rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.2rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><strong>Agenda: </strong>Addressing and resolving the Kashmir conflict</mark></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":4859,"width":530,"height":380,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/new.jpg?w=731" alt="" class="wp-image-4859" style="object-fit:cover;width:530px;height:380px" width="530" height="380" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear delegates,<br>We, Vedika Jain and Priyanka Gupta, hold immense pleasure in welcoming you all to the first ever Shishukunj MUN Jhalaria Junior 2023. We are highly honoured to serve as the co-chairpersons for the Disarmament and International Security Committee(DISEC). A little about us -</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>I, Vedika Jain, am a tenth grader. I love to explore new things and paint out my imagination. As we know that to compete in the contemporary world, it is necessary to have confidence and negotiation skills. Model United Nations is one of the best platforms to start with as it helps in improving deliberating, and collaborating skills and is no less than a knowledge booster. I have participated in several MUNs and I am thrilled to serve this role. I would try my best to make your experience a memorable one.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>I, Priyanka Gupta, am a tenth grader who loves to travel and later paint all the beautiful sceneries I witnessed during the trip. I am a calm person until someone tries to steal my food. Besides that, I attended my first MUN conference in 2021 and I always looked at my seniors working hard to make the MUN a successful one. With that being said, I am thrilled to serve you as the co-chairperson of this committee. You can reach out to any of us to clear out any doubts( we are very friendly).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;Without resolving the Kashmir dispute, lasting peace cannot be acquired in the region. Taking note of this, the agenda of our committee is Addressing and Resolving the Kashmir Conflict. We expect the committee to discuss, debate and find fruitful solutions to deal with this issue.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>We request you interact throughout the committee without hesitating. Furthermore, it is expected that you actively engage in the debates and come to a consensus. We are always there to help you, feel free to approach us regarding any queries.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Wishing you all the very best for this committee session.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Regards<br><strong>Priyanka Gupta and Vedika Jain</strong><br><strong>Co-chairpersons</strong><br><strong>DISEC</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">In 1945, when the charter of the United Nations was signed, the Disarmament and International Security Committee (DISEC) was created as the first committee in the General Assembly (GA). It was created so as to respond to the need to discuss and establish general principles of international peace and security. It deals with the principles governing regulation of arms and weapons. It also seeks out solutions to the challenges in the international security regime. DISEC gives recommendations with regard to such principles to the Security Council. But DISEC cannot directly advise the Security Councils decision-making process.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Addressing and Resolving the Kashmir Conflict</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Since the partition of India in 1947, Kashmir has been a long-disputed region between India and Pakistan which has led to several wars. As the first Kashmir war of 1947 resulted in the death of thousands of people on both sides, India approached the UN with a hope towards peace. As a result, a ceasefire was declared by the UN in 1949.&nbsp;Till date, the nations continue to fight for this strategically important area. To end this conflict the UN has revoked the ceasefire and suggests peaceful resolution of the matter. The committee aims to find solutions regarding the issue.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":2803,"width":205,"height":173,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/study-guide-merged-disec.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/imgonline-com-ua-replacecolor-6obnrjdlcgn.jpg?w=842" alt="" class="wp-image-2803" style="width:205px;height:173px" width="205" height="173" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Study Guide</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3032,"width":168,"height":194,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/disec.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pdf_file_icon.svg_.png?w=640" alt="" class="wp-image-3032" style="width:168px;height:194px" width="168" height="194" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Allotments</strong></figcaption></figure>

  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior IHC]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-ihc/</link>
  <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jun 2023 07:21:30 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=2136</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/hehhh2.png","id":2680,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2680" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/hehhh2.png" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.6rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.6rem"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-background-color"><strong>I</strong>NDIAN <strong>H</strong>ISTORICAL <strong>C</strong>OMMITTEE</mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.2rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center" style="font-size:1.2rem"><mark style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><span style="font-size: 19.2px"><strong>Agenda</strong>:</span> Deliberating upon the formation of nations after independence from the British Raj with special emphasis on princely states</mark></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The Chairperson</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4843,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/dsc_0618-1.jpg?w=842" alt="" class="wp-image-4843" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br>It is my exceptional privilege to welcome you to the first installment of the Junior Shishukunj Model United Nations Conference. I am Aziz Matkawala and I will be serving as the Chairperson for The Indian Historic Committee.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>A bit about myself - I am a tenth grader who aspires to become a corporate lawyer in the future. I have an immense interest in the geopolitical scenarios around the world which is the reason I started taking part in MUNs. I love to watch documentaries on history and geopolitics by creators such as Johnny Harris and movies by Christopher Nolan and Ryan Gosling. You will often find me listening to rap songs by Drake, Eminem, Snoop Dogg and Dr Dre. MUNs have been a big part of my life and have assisted me in improving my research and public speaking skills and I hope they do the same for you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Our agenda is set in the year 1947, A complex time in Indian history when we finally got independence from British rule but with a brutal division of our country. There existed certain areas in our country called the Princely States. These areas were not under direct British control and had sovereign rulers. They were given the choice to Either integrate with India or Pakistan or remain independent. The goal of our committee is to ensure the just division of these states keeping their interests in mind.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Feel free to contact me if you have any doubts and I hope to have the best MUN experience with you all in August</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Regards&nbsp;<br><strong>Aziz Matkawala</strong><br><strong>Chairperson</strong><br><strong>IHC</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Indian Historic Committee is a committee established in the background of the division of the princely states after the partition of India and Pakistan. The freeze date of the committee is 15 August 1947, the day India got independence. The princely states were given the option to join either India or Pakistan or remain independent. The committee consisting the rulers and representatives of various princely states along with the representatives of the INC, Muslim League and British will be required to come to a conclusion about the decision of joining the nation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Agenda : Deliberating upon the formation of nations after independence from the British Raj with special emphasis on princely states</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Indian Historical Committee will discuss the formation of states after independence from the British Raj, with particular emphasis on the princely states. As we all know, India and Pakistan separated on August 15, 1947. About 500 states could not decide whether to join India, Pakistan or operate as a single country. The migration of people has resulted in bloodshed and an extreme humanitarian, religious and economic crisis.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3233,"width":202,"height":203,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1inZUyp45XoRAf867imtoXjiWcP0EHAUa/view?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/unnamed.png?w=498" alt="" class="wp-image-3233" style="width:202px;height:203px" width="202" height="203" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Study Guide</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":3032,"width":177,"height":204,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/ihc.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/pdf_file_icon.svg_.png?w=640" alt="" class="wp-image-3032" style="width:177px;height:204px" width="177" height="204" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>Allotments</strong></figcaption></figure>
