  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior GA]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-ga-2/</link>
  <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jun 2023 17:36:19 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=2210</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/united_nations_general_assembly_hall_3.jpg","id":2194,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2194" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/united_nations_general_assembly_hall_3.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1,"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#0693e3" class="has-inline-color">GENERAL ASSEMBLY </mark></strong></h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":5,"style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"small"} -->
<h5 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><sub>sHISHUKUNJ MUN 2023 | JUNIOR Jhalaria</sub> </mark></strong></h5>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"full","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignfull has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The <strong>Under Secretary General<strong>: General Assembly</strong> </strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":4790,"width":265,"height":325,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/bi22322-2.jpg?w=868" alt="" class="wp-image-4790" style="object-fit:cover;width:265px;height:325px" width="265" height="325" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><br>Dear delegates,<br>I am Dhruv Nyati, the Under-Secretary-General of the General Assembly for the Shishukunj MUN Jhalaria Junior 2023. I am a class 12th PCM student who aims to pursue further studies abroad. I will be pursuing a degree in finance as I believe that possessing knowledge about money and finance is a persons greatest asset. I have been doing MUNs for six years now, and it has taught me a skill set no book can teach - Critical Thinking, Collaboration and Communication. These skills will surely be useful for each one of you.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The General Assembly is one of the six principal organs of the United Nations. It addresses issues of paramount importance ranging from disarmament and human rights violations to inclusivity, development, peace and decolonization. Entailing six main committees, where all 193 member states receive equal representation, it is by far the most representative organ that works towards achieving world peace and harmony, and embodying what the United Nations truly represents.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In the First Edition of the Junior MUN, we have five exuberant committees under GA. FAO 1, FAO 2, UNICEF 1, UNICEF 2 and lastly DISEC. These committees range from topics of agriculture and child rights to the sixty-nine-year-long rivalry between two countries. This MUN is going to be filled with fun, engaging debates and the opportunity to learn. In conclusion, I would like to say that MUN is not about winning or losing; it is about understanding, growing, and making a positive impact on the world.<br><br>Contact me in case of any concerns/queries, I'll be happy to assist.<br><br>Regards<br><strong>Dhruv Nyati</strong><br><strong>Under-Secretary-General: General Assembly</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Committees </strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":2789,"width":170,"height":172,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-fao-i/"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/fao-2.png?w=1008" alt="" class="wp-image-2789" style="width:170px;height:172px" width="170" height="172" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>FAO 1</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":2790,"width":170,"height":172,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-fao-2/"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/fao-3.png?w=1008" alt="" class="wp-image-2790" style="width:170px;height:172px" width="170" height="172" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong>FAO 2</strong></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":1,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h1 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"></h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:image {"id":2791,"width":171,"height":171,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom"} -->

  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/000321121w.jpg","id":2219,"dimRatio":50,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>

<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#0693e3" class="has-inline-color">ECONOMIC &amp; SOCIAL COUNCIL</mark></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":5,"style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"},"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"0","left":"0"}}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"small"} -->
<h5 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><sub>sHISHUKUNJ MUN 2023 | JUNIOR Jhalaria</sub> </mark></strong></h5>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"full","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"},"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"0","left":"0"}}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignfull has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Letter From The <strong>Under Secretary General </strong></strong>: <strong>Economic &amp; Social Council</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:image {"id":3547,"width":214,"height":321,"scale":"cover","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/bi22317.jpg?w=683" alt="" class="wp-image-3547" style="object-fit:cover;width:214px;height:321px" width="214" height="321" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":"700px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"top","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Dear Delegates,<br>I am Harsh Satish, and it is my honour to serve as the Under-Secretary-General of the Economic and Social Council for the very first edition of the Shishukunj MUN Jhalaria Junior.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Im currently a Commerce with Applied Mathematics and Entrepreneurship student in 12th grade. I am an exuberant and confident soul who is ever ready to learn and experience new things. Some of my interests include public speaking, writing, international relations, music and sports. I have been attending MUN conferences since when I was in 8th grade, and my love for them has only escalated. I cant thank these marvellous conferences enough for my confidence, public speaking, communication, and overall world knowledge.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The Economic and Social Council is one of the 6 principal organs of the United Nations. It is at the heart of the United Nations system to advance the three dimensions of sustainable development  economic, social and environmental. It is the central platform for fostering debate and innovative thinking, forging consensus on ways forward, and coordinating efforts to achieve internationally agreed goals.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In this first edition of the Shishukunj MUN Jhalaria Junior, we have 4 exhilarating committees under ECOSOC, namely UNESCO 1, UNESCO 2, WHO 1, and WHO 2. These committees plan to discuss a diversity of topics ranging from Protecting Cultural Heritage, Education Post COVID-19, Medical Tourism and Protection Against Future Pandemics. We are confident that this conference will be a remarkable experience for every single one of you!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Feel free to contact me if you have any doubts or queries, Ill be happy to be of service!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Regards<br><strong>Harsh Satish</strong><br><strong>Under-Secretary-General: Economic &amp; Social Council</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"><strong>Committees </strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2.4rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2.4rem"></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Jhalaria Junior About]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/jhalaria-junior-about/</link>
  <pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 03:19:47 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>ahladmodi48</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=3010</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/dji_0097.jpg","id":3014,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|60","left":"var:preset|spacing|60"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3014" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/dji_0097.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:site-logo {"width":166} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"1054px"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:1054px"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":1011,"textColor":"background","showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","orientation":"horizontal","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fill","flexSize":null},"spacing":{"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"88px"} -->
<div style="height:88px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#0693e3" class="has-inline-color"><strong>ABOUT</strong></mark></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":5,"style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"600"}},"textColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","fontSize":"small"} -->
<h5 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-cyan-bluish-gray-color has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><sub>sHISHUKUNJ MUN 2023 | Jhalaria JUNIOR</sub> </mark></strong></h5>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase"><strong><code><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cecbcc" class="has-inline-color"><sup> </sup></mark></code></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"117px"} -->
<div style="height:117px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong>History</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The Shishukunj Model United Nations emerged in 2015, evolved as a platform for diplomatic deliberation about global issues, and is going to elevate itself in its eighth iteration as a one-of-a-kind conference where students will strive to learn from their peers while finding solutions to issues at handboth from the past and present. This year, the Shishukunj MUN is further divided into Jhalaria Junior and Jhalaria&nbsp;Senior.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong>The UN4MUN Procedure</strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Although most Model UN conferences have adopted the UNA-USA rules of procedure, the UN4MUN procedure remains one of Shishukunj MUNs most proud and significant features. As prescribed by the United Nations Department of Public Information, this procedure ensures that each delegate is of equal importance in the committee, making it a realistic simulation of the United Nations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong><strong>Functional Excellence</strong></strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With an inextinguishable passion for perfection, the Secretariat, Bureau, and Organising Committee of the Shishukunj MUN are sure to make this conference fruitful for every delegate, no matter their experience.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","level":3,"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"2rem"}},"textColor":"vivid-cyan-blue"} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color" style="font-size:2rem"><strong><strong><strong>A Forum for Fundamental Deliberation</strong></strong></strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This year, the junior edition of the Shishukunj MUN brings forward ten innovative committees with agendas spanning across pandemics, wars and making sure that all voices are heard. With the promise of being a forum for healthy debate, this conference is always open to unconventional ideas and questions that aim to change&nbsp;the&nbsp;world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->]]></content:encoded>

  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNDP 2]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/north-campus-undp2/</link>
  <pubDate>Sat, 02 Sep 2023 15:51:44 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=5147</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/undp-2.jpg","id":1973,"dimRatio":60,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1973" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/undp-2.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->

<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"right"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","overlayBackgroundColor":"background","overlayTextColor":"background","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1rem"}}} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"52px"} -->
<div style="height:52px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMME 2</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>educing <strong>A</strong>ir <strong>P</strong>ollution in <strong>C</strong>ities <strong>U</strong>sing <strong>S</strong>ustainable and <strong>M</strong>odern&nbsp;<strong>T</strong>echnology</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"152px"} -->
<div style="height:152px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Committee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) is a global organization that focuses on promoting sustainable development and eradicating poverty worldwide. Operating in over 170 countries, UNDP works closely with governments, civil society, and the private sector to tackle pressing challenges, such as inequality, climate change, and gender empowerment. It provides technical expertise, resources, and policy advice to support countries in achieving their development goals. UNDP plays a crucial role in fostering inclusive growth, resilience, and sustainable development, aiming to improve the lives of people around the world.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : Reducing Air Pollution in Cities Using Sustainable and Modern&nbsp;Technology</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Air pollution is one of the most well-known issues that every nation on Earth has to deal with. It has an impact on the environment, our health, and our way of life as a whole. While there are many potential causes for this pollution, human activity accounts for the majority of them. Since humans have advanced so much, it is only reasonable to assume that they will create technologies to clean up the earth and reduce air pollution. In conclusion, UNDP will try its best to form a resolution that balances the needs of humans and does not compromise the safety of the environment.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1061,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/undp-2-1.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/undp-2.webp?w=139" alt="" class="wp-image-1061" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DFK2jnvO4Nr9C7u3ntcgPMsc64dNkAMhAAwQqEA3dOk/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","fontSize":"2.9rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:2.9rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONS ENVIRONMENT PROGRAMME 2</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>R</strong>educing the <strong>N</strong>egative <strong>I</strong>mpact of <strong>P</strong>lastic on the <strong>E</strong>nvironment</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"222px"} -->
<div style="height:222px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) is the leading global authority on environmental issues. It works to promote sustainable development, protect the environment, and address pressing challenges such as climate change, biodiversity loss, and pollution. UNEP collaborates with governments, organizations, and communities to develop policies, raise awareness, and implement solutions for environmental conservation. Through its programs and initiatives, UNEP plays a crucial role in fostering international cooperation, driving policy changes, and promoting sustainable practices to ensure a healthy and resilient planet for present and future generations.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Reducing the Negative Impact of Plastic on the Environment</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda for UNEP is "Reducing the Negative Effects of Plastic on the Environment". Plastic is the most widely used commodity in the world and is used in the production of practically everything. But the problem with this magic material is that it is non-degradable. It only accumulates in huge heaps and harms all spheres of the ecosystem: the ocean, land, forests, and biodiversity. It kills innocent animals and depletes the soil's quality. Humans also suffer from the negative effects of plastic, as it directly affects the livelihoods of millions of people. Such problems are a hindrance to achieving the sustainable development goals of proper production and consumption, climate change, and life on water and land. The world needs effective solutions that are formed on a global level and implemented with international cooperation to curb this crisis.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":1071,"width":"100px","height":"100px","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/unep-2-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/enep-1.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1071" style="width:100px;height:100px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"78px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17JoyPpHSkyUg0HoHtGOeS9C0RAQyrEHgfeW5M3Q_hKY/edit?usp=sharing"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:78px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>

<item>
  <title><![CDATA[North Campus UNICEF 2]]></title>
  <link>http://shishukunjmun.in/nc-unicef-2/</link>
  <pubDate>Sun, 01 Oct 2023 11:55:54 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>parthagrawal922</dc:creator>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">https://shishukunjmun.in/?page_id=5309</guid>
  <description/>
  <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover {"url":"https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unicef.jpg","id":916,"dimRatio":70,"minHeight":680,"contentPosition":"center center","align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|20","left":"var:preset|spacing|20"}}},"layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover alignfull" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);min-height:680px"><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-70 has-background-dim"></span><img class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-916" alt="" src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/unicef.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" /><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container"><!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"10%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:10%"><!-- wp:image {"id":1670,"width":"151px","height":"151px","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:spacer -->
<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"textTransform":"uppercase","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","fontSize":"3rem"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">United Nations International Children's <br>Emergency Fund 2</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>D</strong>eveloping <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>S</strong>olutions to <strong>P</strong>rotect the <strong>R</strong>ight to <strong>E</strong>ducation of <strong>C</strong>hildren</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"204px"} -->
<div style="height:204px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Commitee Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">UNICEF, the United Nations International Children's Emergency Fund, is a global organization dedicated to advocating for children's rights and ensuring their well-being. Operating in over 190 countries, UNICEF provides humanitarian aid, healthcare, education, and protection to children in need. It works closely with governments, NGOs, and communities to address issues such as child mortality, malnutrition, lack of access to clean water, and inadequate education. Through its programs and initiatives, UNICEF strives to create a world where every child has the opportunity to thrive, grow, and reach their full potential.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>D</strong>eveloping <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>S</strong>olutions to <strong>P</strong>rotect the <strong>R</strong>ight to <strong>E</strong>ducation of <strong>C</strong>hildren</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">Education is one of the most important criteria for economic development in ones country. It has come to our attention that education is not being provided at its best in every part of the world which is a major issue as barriers like gender, poverty, and hunger come in between. Education not being provided leads to an increased crime rate. Developing sustainable solutions to protect the right to education will provide children with access to it and thus will help in future developments. UNICEF is taking action regarding the same and hopes that every child in this world gets access to education.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:image {"id":4592,"width":"130px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized loud"><a href="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/shishukunj_unicef_mun-conference-20231.pdf"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/07/unicef-removebg-preview.png?w=457" alt="" class="wp-image-4592" style="width:130px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Study Guide</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":426,"width":"95px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"custom","className":"loud"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized loud"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17JoyPpHSkyUg0HoHtGOeS9C0RAQyrEHgfeW5M3Q_hKY/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel=" noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/pdf-image.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-426" style="width:95px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Allotments</figcaption></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/05/shishukunj_nc_mun-4.png?w=500" alt="" class="wp-image-1670" style="width:151px;height:151px" /></figure>

<!-- wp:column {"verticalAlignment":"center","width":"90%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center" style="flex-basis:90%"><!-- wp:navigation {"ref":343,"showSubmenuIcon":false,"icon":"menu","layout":{"type":"flex","justifyContent":"right","flexWrap":"wrap"},"fontSize":"small"} /--></div>

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"53px"} -->
<div style="height:53px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"3rem","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"700","textTransform":"uppercase"}}} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center" style="font-size:3rem;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase">UNITED NATIONs COMMISSION FOR SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT 2</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"},"typography":{"fontSize":"1.8rem"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color" style="color:#0eaec8;font-size:1.8rem"><strong>AGENDA</strong> : <strong>I</strong>mplementation of <strong>S</strong>ustainable <strong>D</strong>evelopment <strong>G</strong>oal <strong>4</strong>- <strong>E</strong>ducation</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"153px"} -->
<div style="height:153px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:cover -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","lock":{"move":false,"remove":false},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Letter From The Chairpersons</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":5557,"width":"401px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"thumbnail","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-thumbnail is-resized"><img src="https://shishukunjmun4.files.wordpress.com/2023/10/img_4890.jpg?w=150" alt="" class="wp-image-5557" style="width:401px;height:auto" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"left"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">Dear Delegates,<br><br>Namaste! We, Arnav Shrivastav and Satvik Phalswal, Co-Chairpersons of UNCSocD are tremendously excited to welcome you to the Shishukunj Model United Nations 2023. It is our distinct honor to welcome you to this prestigious conference. We hope this conference will give you new points of outlook towards significant world issues and is an improving and edifying experience.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">I, Arnav Shrivastav, a 12th grader studying commerce with applied mathematics with the view of pursuing CA and CFA in the future. I have this weird inclination of trying to be every possible juniors favourite senior. I am meticulous and coherent, at least thats what my friends say. I consider myself as a congenial person and am sometimes narcissistic too. I am a bit passionate about music, I play guitar and love to listen to various genres of music. I love to travel, but road trips are a different gravy for me. MUNs have always been fun and a great learning experience for me since I was a 7th grader, I have learned a lot from them and would never regret participating in any one of them. DISEC is one of the committees I absolutely love and am very excited to chair.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">I, Satvik Phalswal, am currently in grade XI (PCM with CS) and this is my third year of association with Model United Nation conferences. I have been the Senior Vice-Captain for the Dhyanchand house. My hobbies include activities that give me an adrenaline boost, mountain biking, participating in high endurance activities like marathons and long-distance cycling, reading, and gaining knowledge on global affairs. In the future, I aspire to be a 9 Paratroopers Regiment, Special Forces Commando in the Indian Army.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|background"}}}},"textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color has-link-color">We believe that MUNs are a fascinating platform for bringing together science and international relations because they challenge students to consider scientific solutions to real-world issues and expose them to the current world. We will discuss and debate the specifics of the problem, the various issues, and find solutions for the same. We hope we will be able to make this MUN a memorable learning experience for you all. We will be more than happy to answer your questions before, during, and after the conference.<br>Looking forward to meet&nbsp;you&nbsp;all<br><br>Regards<br>Satvik Phalswal and Arnav Shrivastav<br>Chairpersons<br>United Nations Commission for Social Development 2</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator {"style":{"layout":{"selfStretch":"fixed","flexSize":null}},"className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Organ Description</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The United Nations Commission for Social Development (UNCSocD) is a body dedicated to addressing global social development challenges. It serves as a platform for member states to discuss and formulate policies aimed at promoting social progress, reducing poverty, and improving the well-being of all individuals. The UNCSocD focuses on issues such as poverty eradication, employment generation, social integration, and sustainable development. It plays a crucial role in fostering international cooperation, sharing best practices, and coordinating efforts to create a more inclusive and equitable world for all.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"left","lock":{"move":true,"remove":true},"align":"wide","style":{"color":{"text":"#0eaec8"}},"fontSize":"x-large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-left has-text-color has-x-large-font-size" style="color:#0eaec8"><strong>Agenda : <strong>Implementation of Sustainable Development Goal 4- Education</strong></strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide"><!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"justify","textColor":"background"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-justify has-background-color has-text-color">The agenda for this committee focuses on implementing Sustainable Development Goal 4, Ensuring inclusive and equitable quality education'. This crucial goal aims to ensure inclusive and equitable education for all, promote lifelong learning opportunities, and foster global literacy. The committee will delve into discussions on strategies to enhance educational access, improve educational infrastructure, and develop inclusive educational policies. Delegates will explore innovative solutions to address the challenges of educational inequality, promote education for sustainable development, and strengthen the role of education in achieving overall sustainable development.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:separator {"align":"wide","backgroundColor":"background","className":"is-style-wide"} -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-background-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background-background-color has-background is-style-wide" />
<!-- /wp:separator -->
